NK063(gu)003:1: // gsang ba snying po'i rgyud kyi spyi don sman lung mi bskyod rdo rjes mdzad pa bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)003:3: gang zhig dngos gnyis lam gsum ma lus chos //
NK063(gu)003:4: yod sogs mtha' rnams bral phyir lhun grub pas //
NK063(gu)003:5: de bzhin nyid du mthar son 'bras mchog can //
NK063(gu)003:6: bdun ldan sku lnga'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK063(gu)003:7: de ltar phyogs dus rgyal ba ma lus pa'i //
NK063(gu)003:8: gsung gcig gdul bya blo yi bye brag gis //
NK063(gu)003:9: so sor 'jal ba rig pa'i byin rlabs yin //
NK063(gu)003:10: brgyad ldan rgyud rgyal rdo rje'i tshig la mos //
NK063(gu)003:11: de don dgongs pa phyin ci ma log par //
NK063(gu)003:12: ston mdzad gsum brgyud mtshan ldan bla ma yi //
NK063(gu)003:13: zhabs btud rtsa bshad rgyud rnams spyi don 'di //
NK063(gu)003:14: dus bzhi phyogs bcu kun tu rgyas gyur cig /
NK063(gu)003:15: 'dir rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las rtsa ba'i rgyud gtsor blangs te /
NK063(gu)003:16: rtsa rgyud bshad rgyud gnyis kyi spyi'i don rnam par bzhag pa bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)003:17: bstan pa'am theg pa spyi'i 'byung lugs ltar gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:18: bye brag tu rgyud 'di nyid kyi gnas tshul ltar gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:19: dang po ni gong du bstan nas /
NK063(gu)003:20: 'dir gnyis pa bye brag tu rgyud 'di nyid kyi
NK063(gu)003:21: gnas tshul ltar gtan la dbab pa 'di dag gi
NK063(gu)003:22: brjod bya rnams gsal bar ston pa'i man ngag /
NK063(gu)003:23: thugs thigs dang spar khab las snang ba bzhir bshad de /
NK063(gu)003:25: rang bzhin bde gshegs gdul bya yi //
NK063(gu)003:26: snang ba gsum gyi ngo bo la //
NK063(gu)003:27: rgyud kyi dbye ba rnam par gzhag /
NK063(gu)003:28: gcig la gsum gyi ngo bo yang //
NK063(gu)003:30: des na snang ba bzhi dag tu zhes pas gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:31: zhar byung 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:32: lam gdul bya'i snang ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:33: 'bras bu de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:34: spyan 'grel las rigs sam rnal 'byor gsum du bshad de /
NK063(gu)003:35: tshad ma gsum gyi dngos po yis //
NK063(gu)003:36: rnal 'byor gsum gyi phung po la //
NK063(gu)003:37: rigs dang snang ba'i yan lag bzhag /
NK063(gu)003:38: de nyid thur ma'i mchog tu bshad //
NK063(gu)003:40: mi 'gyur zhing ma chad pa phyi mo'i rigs sam rang bzhin gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK063(gu)003:41: rgyud du byung zhing mi gtong ba rtsol ba'i rigs sam lam gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK063(gu)003:42: rgyud du byung zin pas mthar thug pa 'bras bu'i rigs sam 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK063(gu)003:43: rim gsum dang mngon rtogs las rgyud dam gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du bshad de /
NK063(gu)003:44: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i shes bya rnams //
NK063(gu)003:45: 'bru mthun don tshig shes bya'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:46: dngos po gsum gyi go rim sdeb //
NK063(gu)003:48: gang rtogs bya gzhi'i rgyud dang /
NK063(gu)003:49: gang gis rtogs shing bgrod pa lam gyi rgyud dang /
NK063(gu)003:50: gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud do //
NK063(gu)003:51: de ltar de dag ming gi rnam grangs yin zhing /
NK063(gu)003:52: de dag gi bye brag rnams ldog pa tha dad pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:53: rang bzhin 'khrul pa dang bcas pa'i ldog pa ni rang bzhin gyi snang ba yin la /
NK063(gu)003:54: bsal bya 'khrul pa'i ldog pa ni gnyis pa yin zhing /
NK063(gu)003:55: sel byed kyi ldog pa ni gsum pa /
NK063(gu)003:56: des dag pa'i ldog pa ni 'bras bu de pa'i snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:58: snang ba gsum gyi ngo bo la //
NK063(gu)003:59: rgyud kyi dbye ba rnam par gzhag /
NK063(gu)003:61: rang bzhin gyi snang ba gzhi'i rgyud dang /
NK063(gu)003:62: gdul bya'i snang ba lam gyi rgyud dang /
NK063(gu)003:63: de pa'i snang ba 'bras bu'i rgyud dang gsum du bsdus te shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)003:64: de yang gsang ba brtan pa'i brjod bya rnams spyi thems bzhis 'chad par bshad de /
NK063(gu)003:66: gang du dgos pa gang nges pa //
NK063(gu)003:67: ngo bo dmigs pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:69: gang gis bstan pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:70: gang gis bstan bya'i ngo bo dang /
NK063(gu)003:71: de ltar bstan pa'i sgra don dang /
NK063(gu)003:72: ji snyed bstan pa'i rnam grangs dang /
NK063(gu)003:73: de dag gi don nye bar sbyar ba'i dpyad pa dang lnga lngas 'chad do //
NK063(gu)003:74: de las dang po rang bzhin gyi snang ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:75: ye nas bcing grol med par lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid de bshad pa'i gzhi yin te /
NK063(gu)003:77: bcings med rnam par grol med pa //
NK063(gu)003:78: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK063(gu)003:80: de bshad na gong ltar lnga las /
NK063(gu)003:83: bstan cing mtshon pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:85: gzhi de pa'i ngo bo nyid du gnas pas gang
NK063(gu)003:86: gis de brtags na rtogs su rung la bsgrubs na
NK063(gu)003:90: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK063(gu)003:91: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK063(gu)003:94: 'khor gnyis kyi gong ma'i rang bzhin rtogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:96: gdul bya gnyis la brgyud pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:97: mngon sum sgo nas bstan pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:101: ngo bo thams cad sems nyid de //
NK063(gu)003:104: rigs mi mthun sel ba'i tshul ni //
NK063(gu)003:105: sems tsam pas kun gzhi rnam shes gzung 'dzin gnyis
NK063(gu)003:106: med kyi shes pa don dam gyi dngos por 'dod
NK063(gu)003:107: pa ste / de yang thugs thigs las /
NK063(gu)003:108: de yang 'ching grol gnyis ka'i bdag /
NK063(gu)003:109: me long dwangs ba'i g.ya' bzhin du //
NK063(gu)003:110: phan tshun spangs ba med pa las //
NK063(gu)003:111: byis pa gzhi dang rten zhes smra //
NK063(gu)003:113: rgyas pa'i don lnga pa las /
NK063(gu)003:114: kun gzhi rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK063(gu)003:115: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ba //
NK063(gu)003:117: ngo bo dngos ni bsgrub pa'i don gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:119: rnam rtog kun gzhi ma yin pa //
NK063(gu)003:120: rang bzhin med la don gyi gzhi //
NK063(gu)003:122: chos thams cad sems su dang /
NK063(gu)003:123: de gnyis su med par dang /
NK063(gu)003:124: de lhun gyis grub par bsgrub pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:125: dang po ni 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i
NK063(gu)003:126: chos thams cad rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK063(gu)003:127: yin te / sems las ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan
NK063(gu)003:128: med pa'i phyir rin po che gser gling du phyin
NK063(gu)003:129: yin te / pa bzhin no // de ltar yang /
NK063(gu)003:132: so so'i snang ba thams cad kun //
NK063(gu)003:133: rang rig rgyal por yang dag 'du //
NK063(gu)003:134: rang rig de nyid thams cad yin //
NK063(gu)003:137: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems /
NK063(gu)003:138: de ni lung gi tshad mar gzhag /
NK063(gu)003:141: sems las ma gtogs chos med phyir //
NK063(gu)003:142: sgyu ma'ang rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK063(gu)003:145: sems nyid de snang stong dbyer med pa yin te /
NK063(gu)003:146: gang gis kyang mthar ma thug pa'i phyir chu zla bzhin /
NK063(gu)003:147: de yang don gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)003:148: snang dang mi snang gnyis ka med //
NK063(gu)003:149: yod dang med pa'ang dbyer med do //
NK063(gu)003:150: yang bden pa gnyis su med par mnyam pa zhes bya ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK063(gu)003:152: 'dul byas snang ba'ang rdo rje nyid //
NK063(gu)003:153: yin phyir ngo bo tha dad med //
NK063(gu)003:156: gnyis bral mnyam dang mi mnyam de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK063(gu)003:157: nga med bdag med mtshan ma sna tshogs dbyer med par //
NK063(gu)003:158: stong dang mi stong mi gnas de bzhin nyid du gcig /
NK063(gu)003:161: dbyer med de nyid chos thams cad du lhun gyis grub pa yin te /
NK063(gu)003:162: mtha' bral du gnas pa'i phyir rin po che'i dgongs 'dod bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:164: ye nas lhun grub sangs rgyas chos //
NK063(gu)003:167: a ni stong dang mi stong gi /
NK063(gu)003:168: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK063(gu)003:171: mkhas pas lhun grub sma bsam 'da' //
NK063(gu)003:174: lhun grub ye shes sgron ma nyid //
NK063(gu)003:175: rang bzhin gsal ba spyan gyi mchog /
NK063(gu)003:178: de yang rang bzhin zhes pa phyin ci log gi
NK063(gu)003:179: rgyu rkyen dang yang dag pa'i shes rab dang gtan
NK063(gu)003:180: tshigs la sogs pa khyad par gang du'ang ma byas
NK063(gu)003:182: rgyal 'gros ma mdzad ma bcos par //
NK063(gu)003:183: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med pa'ang //
NK063(gu)003:185: snang ba zhes pa rang snang ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:187: snang stong kun tu gsal ba /
NK063(gu)003:188: rang bzhin ngang gis snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:190: gzhi zhes pa chos thams cad kyi go 'byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:192: tha snyad gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos //
NK063(gu)003:193: ma lus 'byung phyir gzhi zhes bya //
NK063(gu)003:195: spyir rgyud tsam gyi go ba ni dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel ba dang ldan pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:197: 'brel dang ma tshad med pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:198: phun sum tshogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK063(gu)003:200: bye brag tu gzhi'i dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel pa dang ldan pa ni gzhi'i rgyud yin te /
NK063(gu)003:202: rgyud gsum tshang dang der 'brel pas //
NK063(gu)003:203: rang bzhin rgyud kyi ming du grags //
NK063(gu)003:205: de yang dgos pa ni sngar bstan zin la /
NK063(gu)003:206: 'brel ba ni lam dang shes bya shes byed du
NK063(gu)003:207: 'brel zhing 'bras bu de dang de'i bdag nyid du
NK063(gu)003:209: bde gshegs 'bras bu'i snying po nyid //
NK063(gu)003:210: ye nas yin phyir rigs rgyud de //
NK063(gu)003:214: ngo bo'i gzhi dang btags pa'i gzhi //
NK063(gu)003:216: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi dang /
NK063(gu)003:220: de yang rnam gsum gnas tshul gzhag /
NK063(gu)003:221: ces pas lhag pa don dam dang /
NK063(gu)003:224: de yang mtha' thams cad kyi gzhi stong pa'i ldog pa ni bden pa dang po yin te /
NK063(gu)003:226: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med par //
NK063(gu)003:227: rtogs pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK063(gu)003:229: cir yang snang ba'i ldog pa ni bden pa gnyis pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:231: sems nyid chu zla ltar yin pas /
NK063(gu)003:232: cir yang snang zhing cir yang 'grub //
NK063(gu)003:234: de gnyis ngo bo gcig pa'i ldog pa ni bden pa tha ma ste /
NK063(gu)003:236: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:237: sems nyid chos kyi sku ru gnas //
NK063(gu)003:239: de dag theg pa 'og ma pa 'ga' zhig gis
NK063(gu)003:240: ngo bo tha dad par 'dod pa las 'dir dbyer
NK063(gu)003:241: med pa'i phyir lhag pa zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)003:242: 'dir kha cig rang bzhin gyi snang ba gsum du 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)003:243: gnas tshul gyi phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)003:244: der grub pa'i phyir zhe na rtags ma grub la /
NK063(gu)003:245: der bkod pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)003:246: rang bzhin de rtogs par bya ba'i phyir blos sgro
NK063(gu)003:247: btags te gsum du bkod kyang der mi 'gyur na
NK063(gu)003:249: de ni 'di'i le'u gnyis pa nas bcings med ces pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:251: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK063(gu)003:254: a ni stong dang mi stong gi //
NK063(gu)003:256: lnga pa nas gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ces pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:257: drug pa nas ye shes phyogs bzhi zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:258: brgyad pa nas sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:259: bcu gnyis pa nas dus bzhi phyogs bcu zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:260: bcu gsum pa nas dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:261: bcu dgu pa nas mnyam la mnyam par zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:262: tha ma nas kye kye phyogs bcu zhes pas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:265: btags gzhi gnyis su bstan pa'i chos //
NK063(gu)003:268: 'das pa'i btags gzhi ni thun mong gi lam dang
NK063(gu)003:269: 'bras bu bsdus pa rnams yin pa'i phyir shugs la
NK063(gu)003:270: shes par bya'o // 'khor ba'i btags gzhi ni /
NK063(gu)003:272: 'khor ba'i rgyu rkyen ngo bo dang //
NK063(gu)003:273: dpe dang mtshan nyid byed po dang //
NK063(gu)003:274: 'khor tshul nyes pa dus rnams su //
NK063(gu)003:278: tshul dang nyes pa 'grub byed pa //
NK063(gu)003:279: nye bar mtshon pas rnam par dbye //
NK063(gu)003:280: zhor la spyi yis dgos bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:282: dang po rgyu la gnyis las /
NK063(gu)003:284: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad bdag tu rtog pa las byung ba yin te /
NK063(gu)003:286: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros //
NK063(gu)003:288: gnyis pa bye brag gi rgyu ni /
NK063(gu)003:290: rgyur mtshungs lhan cig nyer len pa //
NK063(gu)003:292: brgyud pa'i rgyu ni bde gshegs snying po zhes pa gang gsungs pa nyid do //
NK063(gu)003:294: ma rig pa dang zhes pas gong ma dang lhan cig tu skyes pa'i ma rigs ste /
NK063(gu)003:296: sems rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba yin yang nges
NK063(gu)003:297: pa'i shes pas nges par ma byas pa ni lhan
NK063(gu)003:298: cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:300: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK063(gu)003:301: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas 'khor ba dang lhan cig tu byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:302: bdag dang chos dang dngos po rnams //
NK063(gu)003:303: ngo bo yod la sogs brtags pas //
NK063(gu)003:305: nye bar len pa'i rgyu ni /
NK063(gu)003:306: dge sdig gi bag chags mthu can du gyur pas 'bras bu 'byin la ma rag pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:308: rtog pa'i bag chags stug po yis //
NK063(gu)003:312: rkyen gnyis bstan pa las gsum dang //
NK063(gu)003:313: kun brtags ma rig nyon mongs lnga //
NK063(gu)003:317: dang po ni mi dge bas ngan song du dang /
NK063(gu)003:318: mi g.yo bas khams gong ma gnyis su ste bsam gtan bzhi dang snyoms 'jug bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)003:319: yang na rgyu 'bras lung du ma bstan pa ni shing bzo ba lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)003:320: dge bas mtho ris su skye ba'i rkyen byed pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:322: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK063(gu)003:323: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK063(gu)003:325: gnyis pa ni zhe sdang gis dmyal bar skye ste /
NK063(gu)003:327: thams cad kun la zhe sdang zhing //
NK063(gu)003:328: snying rje yang dag med gyur na //
NK063(gu)003:329: 'di ni mi bzad chen po'i las //
NK063(gu)003:330: dmyal khams bco brgyad dag tu gnas //
NK063(gu)003:332: 'dod chags kyis yi dwags su skye ste /
NK063(gu)003:334: chags med dngos po ma shes shing //
NK063(gu)003:335: ma lus kun tu 'dod chags pas //
NK063(gu)003:336: lus kyis bsgribs dang zas kyis bsgribs //
NK063(gu)003:337: yi dwags chen po'i gnas su skye //
NK063(gu)003:339: gti mug gis byol song du skye ste /
NK063(gu)003:340: chos rnams ma lus thams cad la //
NK063(gu)003:341: shes rab gsal don med pas na //
NK063(gu)003:342: dge sdig gnyis kyi don ma rtogs //
NK063(gu)003:343: 'di ni byol song gnas su skye //
NK063(gu)003:345: nga rgyal gyis lhar skyed ste /
NK063(gu)003:346: mnyam pa'i don nyid ma rtogs shing //
NK063(gu)003:347: tshad med bzhi dang bsam gtan bzhi //
NK063(gu)003:348: rim par so sor bdag 'dzin cing //
NK063(gu)003:349: gzugs sogs rnams la bdag tu rtog /
NK063(gu)003:350: 'di ni tshangs gnas rim par skye //
NK063(gu)003:352: phrag dog gis lha min du skye ste /
NK063(gu)003:353: phrag dog dngos po mi shes shing //
NK063(gu)003:354: nga dang bdag tu 'dzin gyur na //
NK063(gu)003:355: lha ma yin gyi gnas su skye //
NK063(gu)003:356: de nas yi dwags gnas su skye //
NK063(gu)003:358: de dag mnyam pa las mir skye ste /
NK063(gu)003:359: dge bcu dag la gtsor len cing //
NK063(gu)003:360: dge dang mi dge mi mnyam pas //
NK063(gu)003:361: lha dang mi yi skye gnas te //
NK063(gu)003:365: snod bcud du snang zhing zhen pas las dang sdug bsngal du smin pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:367: ngo bo phyi nang 'jig rten gyi //
NK063(gu)003:368: snang dang zhen pa'i chos rnams so //
NK063(gu)003:371: 'khor ba zo chun khyud 'khor dang mched pa r+ts+wa kha'i me lta bu ste /
NK063(gu)003:373: zo chun r+ts+wa sogs me dpe bzhin //
NK063(gu)003:377: skye zhing 'jig pa'i chos dang ldan pa ste //
NK063(gu)003:379: 'jig dang chags dang stongs dang gnas //
NK063(gu)003:380: skye rgas na 'chi bzhi ldan pas //
NK063(gu)003:381: mtshan nyid ther zug ma yin pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:383: drug pa byed pa po ni /
NK063(gu)003:384: 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i byed pa po ni ma bcos rgyun gyi skad cig ma dang /
NK063(gu)003:385: bye brag tu 'khor ba'i byed pa po ni log rtog rgyun gyi skad cig ma ste /
NK063(gu)003:387: rgyun dang bcas pa'i skad cig ma //
NK063(gu)003:388: las kyi byed par brjod pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:392: sa bon la sogs rgyu dang 'brel ba'i chos drug dang /
NK063(gu)003:393: de dag kyang sa yis rten pa sogs rkyen gyis bsdus pa drug go //
NK063(gu)003:394: nang rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis ni ma rig pa la sogs lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i chos so //
NK063(gu)003:396: rten 'brel bcu gnyis tshul dag tu //
NK063(gu)003:400: 'phags pa'i lam dang bral ba dang //
NK063(gu)003:401: sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba ste //
NK063(gu)003:402: nyes pa rnam pa gnyis su gsungs //
NK063(gu)003:403: 'phags lam bral dang sdug bsngal myong //
NK063(gu)003:406: thog ma dang tha ma med pa nas 'khor ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:407: 'dir kha cig 'khor ba la thog tha yod dam med ce na /
NK063(gu)003:408: don gyi'am dus kyi zhes so //
NK063(gu)003:409: dang po brgyud pa'i rgyu de ma rtogs pa ni thog ma yin la /
NK063(gu)003:410: de ni rtogs pa tha ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:412: 'khor ba spyi la'am bye brag la zhes brtag go //
NK063(gu)003:413: dang po ni thog tha gnyis ka med de /
NK063(gu)003:415: srid pa'i 'khor lo thog tha med //
NK063(gu)003:418: gnyis pa ltar na thog ma med kyang tha ma yod de /
NK063(gu)003:419: rgyal bu don grub bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:420: 'o na spyi la'ang yod par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)003:421: spyi bye brag gi mtshan nyid can yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:422: 'bru'i phung po re re nas bgrangs na 'dzad pa bzhin no zhe na /
NK063(gu)003:424: gal te yod na khams gsum gyi sems can mi dmigs par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)003:425: rgyal bu don grub sangs rgyas pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:428: thog ma tha ma med dus nas //
NK063(gu)003:429: yang dag don la rtogs pas nyams //
NK063(gu)003:431: de ni le'u gnyis pa nas /
NK063(gu)003:432: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK063(gu)003:435: ji snyed 'jig rten zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:436: bcu gsum pa nas ma rtogs pa dang zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:437: bco lnga pa nas bdag tu rmongs pa zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:438: tha ma nas gzung 'dzin spros las zhes pas ston /
NK063(gu)003:439: de dag gi don nye bar sbyar ba dpes mtshon te bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:441: gser gyi dpe bzhin gnyis su med //
NK063(gu)003:443: gser gyi sku dang chol zangs chos du mas tha dad kyang gser du gcig pa ltar /
NK063(gu)003:444: btags gzhi chos can dngos po gnyis su ldog pa
NK063(gu)003:445: tha dad kyang rang bzhin gyi snang bar gcig pa
NK063(gu)003:446: yin te / de nyid rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa'i ldog pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:447: gal te tha dad pa zhig na 'khor ba spangs nas 'das pa bsgrub tu med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)003:449: gser la bzo yi rnam par ltar //
NK063(gu)003:450: snang ba dang po rang rig pa //
NK063(gu)003:452: rgyas pa'i nga gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)003:453: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK063(gu)003:454: ye nas ngo bo yod yin na //
NK063(gu)003:455: nyon mongs spong zhing byang bsgrub med //
NK063(gu)003:457: gzhan yang lam dang theg pa rnams don med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)003:458: dung sol tha dad pas sol ba la byi dor byas kyang dkar po mi 'byung ba bzhin te /
NK063(gu)003:459: so so'i rang bzhin nges she na //
NK063(gu)003:460: yang dag lam gyis bcos su med //
NK063(gu)003:461: ces pa bzhin tha dad pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)003:463: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK063(gu)003:465: gnyis pa gdul bya'i snang ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:466: gdul bya blo dang 'tshams par snang ba de bshad pa'i gzhi yin te /
NK063(gu)003:468: de bzhin nyid kyi ma bcos kyang //
NK063(gu)003:469: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK063(gu)003:471: de la bshad na lnga las /
NK063(gu)003:472: dang po dgos pa ni byed pa gnyis dang ldan te /
NK063(gu)003:473: rang bzhin mngon byed ces pas shes bya gzhi'i rgyud shes par byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:475: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK063(gu)003:477: des thob bya 'bras bu'i rgyud shes par byed pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:479: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK063(gu)003:480: gzhan nas yod 'ongs ma yin te //
NK063(gu)003:481: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK063(gu)003:482: de lta bu yi ngang du byung //
NK063(gu)003:484: gnyis pa ngo bo la gnyis las /
NK063(gu)003:486: rnal 'byor pa zhes pas lam pas 'jug cing bgrod par bya ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:488: bgrod dang de chos ldan pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:490: bgrod byed lam pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK063(gu)003:491: skyed byed shes rab gsum gyis bskyed bya sems thun
NK063(gu)003:492: mong thun min la sogs bzhi lnga ci rigs par
NK063(gu)003:493: skye ba dang skyes pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:495: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK063(gu)003:496: sems bzhi skye bar bstan pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:499: lnga sems ldan pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK063(gu)003:500: skye ba'i gzhi dang skye nges pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:503: skye sa rkyen gyi skye tshul dang //
NK063(gu)003:504: skyes pa'i ngo bo sems rim lnga //
NK063(gu)003:508: gzhi dang skabs dang skyer 'gyur sa //
NK063(gu)003:512: 'bras bu nas skye ba gsum las /
NK063(gu)003:514: grub mtha' gang gi yang sgor ma zhugs par 'dir 'jug par nus pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:518: 'og ma dag gi lam nas 'dir 'jug pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:520: thun mong lam lngar bslab pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:523: 'og ma'i 'bras bu mthar phyin nas 'dir 'jug pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:524: 'dir ni gsang chen nges pa ste //
NK063(gu)003:525: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:527: sems skye ba'i rgyu rkyen rgyu dang rkyen du 'brel bas khyad par du byas nas skye ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:528: dang po rgyu la gnyis las /
NK063(gu)003:530: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po khyab byed du yod pa yin te /
NK063(gu)003:532: snying po rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:534: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK063(gu)003:535: de rtogs rung gi blo so sor rtog pa'i shes rab de yin te /
NK063(gu)003:537: thos bsam bsgom pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK063(gu)003:538: rang byung kun ngam 'grub byed phyir //
NK063(gu)003:541: rgyu'i rkyen ni de ma thag pa nyid do //
NK063(gu)003:542: bdag po'i rkyen ni lung man ngag dang ldan pa'i rdo rje slob dpon te /
NK063(gu)003:544: bshes gnyen mgon la lung gnyis thos //
NK063(gu)003:547: mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud man ngag dang bcas pa rnams te /
NK063(gu)003:549: de bdag gsang sogs dmigs pa ste //
NK063(gu)003:551: de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni //
NK063(gu)003:552: thos bsam gyis shes bya la rtogs pa bogs phyung ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:554: skad cig 'phel ba'ang de ma thag /
NK063(gu)003:557: lhan cig byed rgyu dang bcas pa'i lam pa ste
NK063(gu)003:558: mtshungs par ldan pa'i rgyu don gyi bla ma dang
NK063(gu)003:559: byas pa dang mi rtag pa ltar bdag gcig tu
NK063(gu)003:560: 'brel zhing / bdag rkyen rtags kyi bla ma dang
NK063(gu)003:561: snod dang bcud du seng ge'i 'o ma ltar 'brel
NK063(gu)003:562: 'brel zhing / la / dmigs rkyen mdo rgyud rnams
NK063(gu)003:563: dang me ltar shes bya shes byed du 'brel zhing
NK063(gu)003:564: 'brel zhing / la / // de gsung ba po
NK063(gu)003:565: ston pa'i bdag nyid nyi ma dang 'jig rten ltar
NK063(gu)003:566: las dang thugs rjer 'brel ba'i phyir rgyu dang rkyen
NK063(gu)003:567: 'brel zhing / la / // du gyur pa'o // sems skye tshul ni brgyad de /
NK063(gu)003:568: mos pa tha dad kyi sgo nas bzhag pa thabs grol gnyis su dang /
NK063(gu)003:569: blo che chung gi sgo nas rim cig car gnyis su dang /
NK063(gu)003:570: rim pa spangs ma spangs kyi sgo nas mthar chags thod rgal gnyis su dang /
NK063(gu)003:571: zhen pa dag ma dag gi sgo nas zag bcas zag med gnyis su dang /
NK063(gu)003:572: mtshan ma che chung gi sgo nas mi rtog pa dang lha sgom pa dang gnyis su dang /
NK063(gu)003:573: phan gdags pa dang gdul dka' 'dul ba'i sgo nas zhi ba dang khro bo gnyis su dang /
NK063(gu)003:574: ting nge 'dzin gsal mi gsal gyi sgo nas mos
NK063(gu)003:575: bsgom dang yongs rdzogs su bsgom pa gnyis su dang
NK063(gu)003:576: / rang stobs gzhan stobs kyi sgo nas gdams ngag dang shes rab tu sems skye ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:577: skyes pa rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK063(gu)003:578: ngo bo sems lnga skye ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:581: ngo bo rkyen gyis rnam par dbye //
NK063(gu)003:582: rigs dang rigs su nges pa yi //
NK063(gu)003:583: zhes pas grol lam gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:586: 'jig dang ldang dang gnas pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:587: smon pa byang chub sems yin no //
NK063(gu)003:588: g.yo dang bskyod dang ldang dang gnas //
NK063(gu)003:591: brtags pa gnyis zhig nas gsang sngags su g.yo ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:592: gzhi des khong du chud par smon pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:594: don nyams su len cing gnas pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:595: de mthar phyin pa'i sems te /
NK063(gu)003:597: de ji bzhin du gnyis dang bzhi //
NK063(gu)003:599: gzhi de khong du smon pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:600: lhag pa gzugs brnyan 'jug par byed //
NK063(gu)003:601: mchog gi dam tshig de ru sbyin //
NK063(gu)003:602: rigs nges gyur la phan pa bcu //
NK063(gu)003:603: nus pa gnyis kyi byin rlabs bzhag /
NK063(gu)003:604: rang gi spyan mchog byed la brtson //
NK063(gu)003:606: gnyis pa ni khog gzhung las /
NK063(gu)003:607: de yang skye bo chags can don //
NK063(gu)003:608: zhes pas 'og sgo'i sems lnga ste /
NK063(gu)003:615: 'jig ldang la sogs byang sems lnga //
NK063(gu)003:616: nges par skyes pa ngo bor bshad //
NK063(gu)003:618: gsum pa sgra bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:619: de yang gdul bya zhes pa thun mong dang mchog gi sems lnga skyer rung ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:621: phye bas rgyu 'bras chen po dag /
NK063(gu)003:624: snang ba zhes pa bstan pa blo dang 'tshams pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:626: bla med theg pa bsam yas gsungs pa yang //
NK063(gu)003:627: so so rang gi blo la snang bar zad //
NK063(gu)003:629: lam gyi rgyud ces pa ni lam 'di gzhi shes shing 'bras bu thob byed yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:630: shes bya dang thob byed gnyis kyi ming gis btags
NK063(gu)003:631: pas lam gyi rgyud yin pa'i phyir btags pa las
NK063(gu)003:634: shes thob btags ming nges tshig gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:636: yang lam gyi cha rkyen gyi dgos pa dang ldan
NK063(gu)003:637: zhing gzhi lam shes bya shes byed du 'brel la
NK063(gu)003:638: / lam 'bras thob bya thob byed du 'brel ba'i
NK063(gu)003:639: phyir lam gyi rgyud yin pa'i phyir rang gi ngo
NK063(gu)003:640: bos thob pa zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)003:642: rgyu rkyen thabs 'brel dgos rdzogs phyir //
NK063(gu)003:645: rang gi nges tshig bzhi ru 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:649: thun mong lam lngar bslab pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:650: khyad par so so'i lam bzhin bslab //
NK063(gu)003:651: ces pas thun mong gi dang /
NK063(gu)003:652: thun mong ma yin pa'i lam gnyis so //
NK063(gu)003:655: dngos su 'di'i gool sa shes shing brgyud nas gdul
NK063(gu)003:656: bya dman pa'ang khyad par gyi lam la gzud pa
NK063(gu)003:658: thun mong lam stegs tsam nyid du //
NK063(gu)003:659: pha rol phyin bcu rgyu 'bras spyod //
NK063(gu)003:661: ngo bo ni gang blo che chung gi yul du gyur pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:662: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi dang phyi rgyud sde gsum mo //
NK063(gu)003:664: de dag gis rang rang gi 'bras bu bsgrub pa
NK063(gu)003:665: dang 'di'i lam stegs su bgrod pa thun mong du
NK063(gu)003:669: ltos pas thun mong gi lam mo //
NK063(gu)003:671: lha mi nyan rang sems dpa' bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)003:673: rigs kyi dbye bas lam phye ba //
NK063(gu)003:675: ma nges spyi yi dbye ba ste //
NK063(gu)003:676: bzhi ni nges 'byung thun mong lam //
NK063(gu)003:679: kri ya yo ga u pa gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:680: de bzhin rigs gcig thun mong min //
NK063(gu)003:681: de nyid phyi nang cha phye bas //
NK063(gu)003:682: phyi rol ltos pas thun mong lam //
NK063(gu)003:684: de dag 'di'i nyams su blang bya yin nam ma yin na /
NK063(gu)003:685: dngos su min cing rim gyis pa ltos nas shugs la sngon du rdzogs par bya ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:687: rang bzhin sngon du song ba dang //
NK063(gu)003:688: ched du mngon du bsdur bas 'gro //
NK063(gu)003:689: des na thun mong mngon rdzogs lam //
NK063(gu)003:691: de ni gsum pa nas thams cad kyang 'di lta ste /
NK063(gu)003:693: drug pa nas de nas sa bcu rim gyis 'byang /
NK063(gu)003:695: bcu gsum pa nas ma rtogs pa dang zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:697: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK063(gu)003:699: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i lam ni /
NK063(gu)003:701: thun mong ma yin rnam gnyis te //
NK063(gu)003:705: grol lam thabs su rnam par bshad //
NK063(gu)003:707: shes rab grol ba'i lam dang /
NK063(gu)003:708: thabs kyi lam ste 'og tu ston no //
NK063(gu)003:709: tha ma de dag gi don nye bar sbyar ba'i bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:710: lam de mtshon par byed pa'i gzhung tshogs yi ge'i rgyud kyi bshad thabs te /
NK063(gu)003:712: tshig dang yi ge'i rkyen gnyis la //
NK063(gu)003:713: brten nas rtogs par byed pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:716: gang bshad par bya ba'i rgyud ngos gzung ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:717: de ji ltar bshad pa'i thabs so //
NK063(gu)003:718: dang po ni rgyud thams cad la /
NK063(gu)003:719: thabs kyi rgyud ni brjod bya'i gtso bo bde stong gnyis las bde ba /
NK063(gu)003:720: byams snying gnyis las byams pa /
NK063(gu)003:722: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo yang yab shas che bas thabs kyi rgyud do //
NK063(gu)003:723: brjod bya'i gtso bo bde stong gnyis las stong pa /
NK063(gu)003:724: byams snying gnyis las snying rje /
NK063(gu)003:725: rtsa thig gnyis las thig le /
NK063(gu)003:726: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo yum shas che bas shes rab kyi rgyud do //
NK063(gu)003:727: gzhan yang gdul bya skyes pa dang bud med kyi ched du rgyud gnyis su nges te /
NK063(gu)003:728: skyes pa rnams ni 'dul don du //
NK063(gu)003:729: thabs kyi rgyud rnams rab bshad la //
NK063(gu)003:730: btsun mo rnams ni bsdu ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:731: shes rab ma yi rgyud rab bshad //
NK063(gu)003:733: brjod bya'o gtso bo bde stong dbyer med /
NK063(gu)003:736: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo yang yab yum zhal sbyor bas dbyer med du nges pas te /
NK063(gu)003:738: thabs dang shes rab ma ning rgyud //
NK063(gu)003:739: bstan pa'i yig lam rkyen du 'dod //
NK063(gu)003:741: 'di ni dbyer med kyi rgyud de /
NK063(gu)003:742: rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi sbyi /
NK063(gu)003:744: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK063(gu)003:745: dam tshig bsgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:746: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK063(gu)003:747: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK063(gu)003:748: zhes pa ltar gzhung gzhan la ma brten par don gzhan bskyed nus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud 'di dang /
NK063(gu)003:749: rgyud kyis rgyud kyi don 'grol ba bshad pa'i rgyud dang /
NK063(gu)003:750: de dag gi ma tshang ba kha skong ba rgyud phyi ma rnams la sa /
NK063(gu)003:751: dngos su dang po yin la shugs la gang bshad byar ngos gzung ngo //
NK063(gu)003:752: gnyis pa de bshad thabs la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:753: dor bya bshad tshul nyes pa'i skyon ngos gzung ba ni brgyad de /
NK063(gu)003:754: sngags dang mtshan nyid bsres nas bshad na rdo rje theg pa na babs kyi skyon dang /
NK063(gu)003:755: yo ga phyi nang bsres na khyad par bsnyen sgrub kyi don las 'brog 'chol ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:756: rtog ge bas btags pa'i the tshom gyi gegs sel ma shes na mdzangs pa lce rdum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:757: rgyud 'khrugs pa'i bdag nyid sdeb ma shes na rat+na rtsar 'chol gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:758: 'brel tshul gnyis ka mi ldan na rang dag'i tshig dang /
NK063(gu)003:759: mi mthun pa'i tshig don sdeb ma shes na shes rab long ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:760: mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa sdeb ma shes na bdud rtsi ro nyams kyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:761: spyi dang khyad par gyi dgos ched med na don med 'chal ba'i skyon no //
NK063(gu)003:762: dang du blang ba legs pa'i yon tan shes par bya ba ni bcu gcig ste /
NK063(gu)003:763: lta ba brgal brtag gis bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:764: spyod pa rjes 'jug thabs kyis dang /
NK063(gu)003:766: dam tshig rnam grangs kyis dang /
NK063(gu)003:767: phrin las chog bsgrigs kyis dang /
NK063(gu)003:768: sgrub pa phyag bzhes kyis dang /
NK063(gu)003:770: p+au dza phyi nang gis dang /
NK063(gu)003:771: sngags sgra dang sdeb kyis dang /
NK063(gu)003:772: phyag rgya bskyed rim gyis bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:773: des ji ltar rtogs tshul dpe'i sgo nas bstan pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:775: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK063(gu)003:778: dbang po rab la rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pas rtogs
NK063(gu)003:779: pa sman pa 'tsho byed kyis lag gi rtsa bltas
NK063(gu)003:780: pas lus mgo mjug gi nad rtogs pa lta bu
NK063(gu)003:781: dang / 'bring gi don rnam par phye bas rtogs pa sman snod kyi kha byang lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)003:782: tha ma la 'bru re gnyer res rtogs pas sman
NK063(gu)003:783: gcig gcig kyang dri dang kha dog la sogs pa
NK063(gu)003:784: chos du mas gtan la 'bebs pa lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)003:787: rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK063(gu)003:790: dang por mtshon pa mtshan gsum ldan //
NK063(gu)003:792: bstan bya mtshan gyi rnam grangs gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:794: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK063(gu)003:796: rgyud dang ston pa'i mtshan thun mong du grags pa rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:798: rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK063(gu)003:799: bde ldan gsung gi don 'byung ba //
NK063(gu)003:801: lung dang che ba las btags pa lung gi spyi zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)003:803: lung gi spyi 'di yang shin tu zab pa'i phyir zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:805: rgyud dang lung gi spyi zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:807: lung gi spyi ru grags pa 'di zhes so //
NK063(gu)003:808: man ngag dang don rang gi ngo bo la btags pa gsang ba'i snying po ste /
NK063(gu)003:810: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK063(gu)003:813: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK063(gu)003:814: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK063(gu)003:816: de dag gi dpe gong du smos pa ltar dbang
NK063(gu)003:817: po rab la ltos nas rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don
NK063(gu)003:820: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK063(gu)003:821: skal ba can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:823: gnyis pa don rnam par dbye ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:825: lung gi spyi ru grags pa 'di //
NK063(gu)003:826: rnam par phye pas lnga ru 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:830: rgyud gzhung gzhi bslang yongs su shes //
NK063(gu)003:833: rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng gzhi dang /
NK063(gu)003:840: rgyud don 'byung bar nges shing des ma 'ongs pa'i gdul bya rnams yid ches pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:841: ngo bo ni phun sum tshogs pa lnga ste 'og tu ston /
NK063(gu)003:843: gleng ba zhes pa rgyud 'chad pa yin /
NK063(gu)003:844: de'i rgyu'am gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:847: thun mong gleng gzhi rnam gnyis dang //
NK063(gu)003:848: thun mong min pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:851: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi gnyis so //
NK063(gu)003:854: rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can gyi'o //
NK063(gu)003:858: zhor la dus lugs bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:860: nyid kyi sku gsung thugs las thub pa drug spros pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:862: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la thugs
NK063(gu)003:863: rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs zhes bya ba'i rig
NK063(gu)003:864: pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug de pa thams cad
NK063(gu)003:865: kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'thon
NK063(gu)003:868: thub drug ston pa zhes pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:871: stong gsum gnas pa zhes pa zhing khams te /
NK063(gu)003:872: 'thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gis s+n+rel gzhi dang
NK063(gu)003:873: yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha'
NK063(gu)003:874: yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK063(gu)003:876: khyad par sh+aakya thub pa nyid ces pa ston pa
NK063(gu)003:877: ste thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res
NK063(gu)003:879: rgyud drug 'khor dang rnam bzhi sogs //
NK063(gu)003:882: 'gro ba lnga yi don mdzad de //
NK063(gu)003:885: rgyal srid btsun mo 'khor spangs nas //
NK063(gu)003:886: rab tu byung sogs mdzad pa yi //
NK063(gu)003:892: thugs kyi ni dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa zhes so //
NK063(gu)003:893: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ni kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab ces so //
NK063(gu)003:894: gsung gi mdzad pa ni thams cad kyang 'di lta ste 'dul ba'i dbang gis zhes pas so //
NK063(gu)003:895: dus ni sgron ma bkod pa'i dus te /
NK063(gu)003:897: shin tu dkon pa'i dus na'o //
NK063(gu)003:900: skye bo chags sogs spong 'dul ba //
NK063(gu)003:901: byin rlabs shar ba'i thub pa nyid //
NK063(gu)003:902: mi yi skye ba bzhes snang bas //
NK063(gu)003:903: bcu gnyis la sogs rdzogs pa ste //
NK063(gu)003:904: rnam dag mchod rten rdo rje'i gdan //
NK063(gu)003:905: rab byung mngon par rdzogs tshul snang //
NK063(gu)003:907: de ni le'u gsum pa'i stod nas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:908: gnyis pa rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can gyi gleng gzhi la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)003:910: zhor la gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK063(gu)003:913: ston pa gnas dang sdud pa 'khor //
NK063(gu)003:914: zhes pas de dag 'dzom pa'i tshe dus te /
NK063(gu)003:915: phun sum tshogs pa lnga las /
NK063(gu)003:920: bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po yab yum ste /
NK063(gu)003:922: ston pa'i rang bzhin bdun dang ldan //
NK063(gu)003:923: bdag nyid byed pa kun tu bzang //
NK063(gu)003:925: gnyis pa ni rigs lnga yab yum ste /
NK063(gu)003:927: mtshungs pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:928: lngas kyang ston pa gsung mi 'gal //
NK063(gu)003:930: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK063(gu)003:932: gnas ni 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang ste /
NK063(gu)003:934: gnas kyi rang bzhin de bzhin nyid //
NK063(gu)003:935: ngo bo 'og min gzhal yas khang //
NK063(gu)003:937: yang 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)003:938: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa na /
NK063(gu)003:941: chos dbyings 'og min gsang ba na //
NK063(gu)003:942: lhan cig 'dus pa'i rin chen khang //
NK063(gu)003:946: zhor la de dag gi tshad do //
NK063(gu)003:949: lhan cig 'khor dang go phye ba //
NK063(gu)003:954: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa ni gong du bstan pa 'chad pa'i skyes bu lnga ste /
NK063(gu)003:956: nyid las mi gzhan rigs lnga dang //
NK063(gu)003:958: rig pa khyad par can gyi ni rgyal sras sems dpa' dang 'jigs byed chen po rnams te /
NK063(gu)003:960: rig pa'i ye shes byang chub sems //
NK063(gu)003:962: de nas byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:963: zhes pa nas mtshan mar ma yin pa la sogs pa zhes so //
NK063(gu)003:964: chos kyi 'brel ba dad pas gtam nyan pa'i 'khor ni /
NK063(gu)003:965: 'jig rten pa'i lha chen po la sogs pa rnams te /
NK063(gu)003:966: dad pas nyan pa'i lha chen rnams //
NK063(gu)003:968: rgyas pa'i don gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)003:969: gong na med pa'i ye shes mchog /
NK063(gu)003:970: thams cad la ni dbang sgyur phyir //
NK063(gu)003:971: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyi bskor //
NK063(gu)003:974: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i bla med rjes mdong dang //
NK063(gu)003:975: 'jig rten gtso dang 'khor bkur dbang phyug dang //
NK063(gu)003:977: gnyis pa go phye ba'i 'khor ni //
NK063(gu)003:978: thun mong ba rnam par 'dren pa'i sprul pa drug dang /
NK063(gu)003:979: rjes su 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor pa skal pa can rnams te /
NK063(gu)003:980: 'gro ba 'dul bar sprul sogs pa zhes pas /
NK063(gu)003:981: rgyas pa'i bcu gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)003:982: gzhan yang phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khams rnams na //
NK063(gu)003:987: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:988: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK063(gu)003:989: zhes pa rnams ni go phye bar mang mngon no //
NK063(gu)003:991: kun tu khyab cing mtha' yas par khyab pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:992: chos kyi dbyings mtha' yas par khyab pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK063(gu)003:993: dper na til gyi gang bu bzhin du gang nas khyab par bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)003:995: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)003:997: 'khor gyi tshad ni khyab dang mang //
NK063(gu)003:998: brjod 'das nam mkha'i mtha' klas gang //
NK063(gu)003:1002: gdul bya la snang ba'i dus so //
NK063(gu)003:1004: snga phyi tha dad du 'dzin pa 'khrul pa yin la de dag pas mnyam pa nyid de /
NK063(gu)003:1006: dus kyi ngo bo mnyam gnas kyang //
NK063(gu)003:1010: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par las //
NK063(gu)003:1011: dus bzhi snga phyi med pa yi //
NK063(gu)003:1012: mnyam pa nyid du lhan ner sbyor //
NK063(gu)003:1014: 'di nas dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang zhes so //
NK063(gu)003:1016: rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu phun sum tshogs pa lnga po
NK063(gu)003:1017: tshang bas gdul bya'i ngo la rgyud don byung ba
NK063(gu)003:1018: de yin te / de nyid las /
NK063(gu)003:1019: skal pa can las dkon pa'i dus //
NK063(gu)003:1022: phyos bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba rnams kyi gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin pa gsang bdag ste /
NK063(gu)003:1024: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK063(gu)003:1025: thun mong ma yin nges pa'i rgyud //
NK063(gu)003:1026: dris lan mi mngon don gyis bsdus //
NK063(gu)003:1027: byin rlabs mi yul grags pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:1030: 'khor gyi nang nas skal ldan mchog /
NK063(gu)003:1031: 'dul ba'i dus bab gsang ba'i bdag /
NK063(gu)003:1032: lag na rdo rjes bsdu ba mdzad //
NK063(gu)003:1035: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK063(gu)003:1037: de le'u dang pos ston no //
NK063(gu)003:1038: gnyis pa gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gzhi la yang lnga las /
NK063(gu)003:1040: gong ma nyid khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du mngon par
NK063(gu)003:1041: 'du mdzad pa ste che mchog badz+ra he ru ka
NK063(gu)003:1043: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag pos sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo'o //
NK063(gu)003:1044: gnas ni dur khrod chen po'i dkyil 'khor te bde ba'i gnas zhes pas /
NK063(gu)003:1045: dur khrod chen por bzhugs par dgyes nas khrag gi
NK063(gu)003:1046: rgya mtsho'i dkyil keng rus chen po ri rab kyi
NK063(gu)003:1050: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen por gyur te shar phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)003:1051: gsang ba'i bu mo brgyad ni /
NK063(gu)003:1052: dkar mo'i tshogs dang zhes pa la sogs so //
NK063(gu)003:1053: gus pa'i bu mo brgyad ni /
NK063(gu)003:1054: seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs la sogs so //
NK063(gu)003:1055: dur khrod sa'i sgo srung bzhi ni /
NK063(gu)003:1056: stag gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang zhes so //
NK063(gu)003:1058: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo la sogs so //
NK063(gu)003:1060: gdul dka' drag po'i gdul bya las drag po'i phrin las su snang ba'i dus te /
NK063(gu)003:1061: 'dul ba'i thabs sna tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab par so sor snang bas dus gcig tu btul te /
NK063(gu)003:1063: sdud pa po ni gong ma'o //
NK063(gu)003:1065: gnyis pa thun mun gyi gleng gzhi la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)003:1066: spyir bskyed rdzogs gnyis las rdzogs rim gyi char gtogs pas na /
NK063(gu)003:1067: rdzogs pa bskyed rim gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:1068: rdzogs pa rdzogs rim gyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK063(gu)003:1070: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab bzhi las
NK063(gu)003:1071: bzhi'i dbyibs dang kha dog tu yod pa ni gnas
NK063(gu)003:1074: 'od bzhin e sogs dbyibs can gnas //
NK063(gu)003:1076: de'i dbus na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le ni ston no //
NK063(gu)003:1078: mi shigs thig le bam dbyibs can //
NK063(gu)003:1079: rang la bde ba gsal byed bdag /
NK063(gu)003:1081: ye shes la sogs bde ba'i rnam shes skyer rung ba ni 'khor zhes pas /
NK063(gu)003:1083: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK063(gu)003:1084: ye shes myong bas bshad sdud 'dod //
NK063(gu)003:1086: don dam byang sems dngos su skyes pa ni sdud
NK063(gu)003:1087: pa po yang yin la bstan par yang rung ste
NK063(gu)003:1088: / ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa /
NK063(gu)003:1089: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK063(gu)003:1091: de'i tshe snga phyir 'dzin pa dag pas dus zhes pas /
NK063(gu)003:1092: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK063(gu)003:1093: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK063(gu)003:1095: gnyis pa ni yum gyi mkha' las bzhi'i dbyibs su yod pa ni gnas te /
NK063(gu)003:1097: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK063(gu)003:1098: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs su gnas //
NK063(gu)003:1100: yab kyi thig le dbur rdzogs pa ni thams cad kyi byed pa po'i phyir ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1102: skad cig gsal byed las ming can //
NK063(gu)003:1103: bam dbyibs thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1105: ye shes la sogs gsang ba'i rnam shes myong byed ni 'khor te /
NK063(gu)003:1107: ma da ma nu sdom byed yi //
NK063(gu)003:1108: lus can rnam shes de dag la //
NK063(gu)003:1110: thams cad bde bar bsdus nas dngos su nyams su myong bas sdud par yang rung la /
NK063(gu)003:1111: myong bya don zab mo ni bstan pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1112: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK063(gu)003:1113: ya na theg chen 'di nyid do //
NK063(gu)003:1115: de skyes la ngos mi zin pa ni bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i phyir dus te /
NK063(gu)003:1116: dus ni bsam gyi mi khyab dus //
NK063(gu)003:1117: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya ba //
NK063(gu)003:1120: yab yum rol pa'i dus nyid du //
NK063(gu)003:1121: gsang ba phun sum tshogs drug gis //
NK063(gu)003:1122: yig bzhi'i sgo nas byin brlabs kyis //
NK063(gu)003:1123: dbang bskur ma brjod rgyud bshad pa //
NK063(gu)003:1124: kun yul min pas skal med gsang //
NK063(gu)003:1128: bcu gsum pa rnams nas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:1129: don gnyis pa rkyen gling bslang ba la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)003:1131: myur du rgyud don gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par 'byung ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:1133: brjod bya rang bzhin gsang ba'i rgyud //
NK063(gu)003:1134: de ji bzhin du rjod byed dag /
NK063(gu)003:1135: ston pas rgyud don lam dang tshig /
NK063(gu)003:1136: gleng gzhi'i rjes su nges par 'gro //
NK063(gu)003:1139: ston 'khor dris lan gcig gi rkyen du gcig gyur pas bstan pa 'byung la ma rag pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1141: ston pas gnang dang 'khor gyis zhus //
NK063(gu)003:1142: skabs las gleng bslang ston dang 'khor //
NK063(gu)003:1143: gnang 'dri'i rkyen du gang gyur pa //
NK063(gu)003:1144: de des gsung la ma reg pa //
NK063(gu)003:1147: gong ltar gleng ba ni rgyud 'chad pa yin la /
NK063(gu)003:1148: der bskul bas rgyud 'byung ba'i rkyen du gyur pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:1150: nges pa'i tshig grub ngo bo'ang de //
NK063(gu)003:1151: skabs kyi dris las smos ci dgos //
NK063(gu)003:1152: dris las mdo phyir nges par 'grub //
NK063(gu)003:1156: de bzhin gleng bslang rnam pa gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:1158: thun min lhan cig pa'i ched du dang /
NK063(gu)003:1159: thun mong gi phye ba'i ched du gleng bslang ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:1161: 'khor dang gzhan gyi don phyir dang //
NK063(gu)003:1162: rgyu tshogs thugs rjes ldang par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:1165: gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:1166: dbang phyi ma gnyis kyi byed las thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1169: thun mong ma yin ston pa gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:1170: yab yum chags bskul rol pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:1171: dgyes bstar 'khor la dbang bskur bas //
NK063(gu)003:1172: rgyud don 'byung phyir bslang zhes bya //
NK063(gu)003:1173: zhes pas yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1175: de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje
NK063(gu)003:1176: yid kun tu bzang po thams cad ma lus pa'i
NK063(gu)003:1177: rang bzhin gyi tshul rdo rje btsun mo bya ba
NK063(gu)003:1178: mo chos sku kun tu bzang mo la 'jug par
NK063(gu)003:1179: gyur to // nyams su bstar ba las khyad par gyi rdzas kyi dbang bskur ba dngos ni /
NK063(gu)003:1180: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de pa ma lus pa thams cad gcig gi rang bzhin du dbyer med pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1181: gleng bslang nas de'i rtogs pa brjod pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1182: e ma hoh rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK063(gu)003:1185: phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben //
NK063(gu)003:1188: de pa nyid kyis de pa nyid la ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK063(gu)003:1189: zhes brjod pas thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen to //
NK063(gu)003:1192: de nas gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen pos
NK063(gu)003:1193: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i sems ye shes su bskyed
NK063(gu)003:1195: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK063(gu)003:1196: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK063(gu)003:1197: skye ba med las zhes g.yo ldang dang /
NK063(gu)003:1199: gnas pa med las zhes gnas pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:1200: dmigs pa med las zhes smon pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:1201: 'gro 'ong med las zhes 'gro 'ong byang sems so //
NK063(gu)003:1202: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod de dbang gi ngo
NK063(gu)003:1203: bo thabs lam gyi sems rim pa lngar bskyed nas
NK063(gu)003:1204: de thob pa'i yon tan ston 'khor dgongs pa tha
NK063(gu)003:1205: mi dad du gyur pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1206: zhes brjod pas de pa thams cad dang btsun mo'i
NK063(gu)003:1207: tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad mnyes pas khyad par
NK063(gu)003:1209: 'gro ba chags can spongs med la //
NK063(gu)003:1210: longs spyod rdzogs sku btsun mo dang //
NK063(gu)003:1211: gnyis med rol sogs bstan pa ste //
NK063(gu)003:1212: mthun pas mthun pa sgrol phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1216: thun mong gleng bslang ston dang 'khor //
NK063(gu)003:1217: tha dad snang nas dbang thob ste //
NK063(gu)003:1218: nyid kyis rtogs nas 'gro don du //
NK063(gu)003:1219: bka' stsal don gyis zhus dang lan //
NK063(gu)003:1220: zhes pas lhan cig pa rnams dbang thob pas rgyud
NK063(gu)003:1221: rtogs kyang go phye ba gsang ba bzhis bsgrags pa'i
NK063(gu)003:1222: ched du de bshad par zhus pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1223: de nas de pa thams cad btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK063(gu)003:1224: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK063(gu)003:1225: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK063(gu)003:1226: ngo bo nyid kyi rab tu gsang //
NK063(gu)003:1227: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK063(gu)003:1230: gnang bar don gyi tshig tu phyung //
NK063(gu)003:1231: sku gsung thugs kyi spro ba mdzad //
NK063(gu)003:1233: ces brjod pas zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:1234: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK063(gu)003:1235: e ma ho zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)003:1236: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK063(gu)003:1237: ces pa'i bar gyis ston pa thugs rje skyes nas rgyud 'chad par dgyes pa mdzad pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1239: don gsum pa yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po rgyud kyi don la yang bzhi las /
NK063(gu)003:1241: dngos su lam gyi rgyud rtogs shing brgyud nas gnas
NK063(gu)003:1242: skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu gnyis mngon du
NK063(gu)003:1243: byed pa'o // ngo bo ni lam dang de'i cha rkyen rnams te 'og tu ston no //
NK063(gu)003:1245: rgyud ces pa gong ltar la /
NK063(gu)003:1246: don zhes pa bya ba'i sgra byed pa la zhugs
NK063(gu)003:1247: pa ste shes bya dang thob bya ni don yin
NK063(gu)003:1248: la / de lam 'dis shes shing thob par byed pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:1250: rgyud don tshang dang don 'brel bas //
NK063(gu)003:1251: rang bzhin rgyud kyi ming du grags //
NK063(gu)003:1252: mtshon byed rgyud kyang de bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:1256: rgyud don lam dang yan lag ste //
NK063(gu)003:1261: khyad par lam gyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK063(gu)003:1263: phye ba'i chos 'brel lam tha dad brtag pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:1266: khyad par gyi lam pas nyams su blang byar gyur pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1268: de ltar brtags pa'i skal ldan phyir //
NK063(gu)003:1270: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK063(gu)003:1271: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas pa //
NK063(gu)003:1275: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul 'di //
NK063(gu)003:1276: skyes bu blo rtsal rab kyis rtogs //
NK063(gu)003:1280: de yang gdul bya'i bsam pa yi //
NK063(gu)003:1281: dbang gis lam yang gnyis su brjod //
NK063(gu)003:1285: grol lam thabs lam bstan pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:1286: zhes pas shes rab grol ba'i lam dang /
NK063(gu)003:1287: gdams ngag thabs kyi lam ste /
NK063(gu)003:1289: shes rab dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK063(gu)003:1290: thabs kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:1296: shes 'jug gi 'ching ba las grol bas 'bras bu grub byed du gyur pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1298: thos bsam bsgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK063(gu)003:1299: rang byung kun ngam 'grub byed phyir //
NK063(gu)003:1303: ring ba'ang rim dang cig car ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1304: zhes pas rim gyis pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:1307: lam mtshan nyid gsum du bcing ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:1308: de la mthar chags thod rgal du brtag pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:1309: lam gang la zhi khro gnyis su yod med kyi bye brag dang /
NK063(gu)003:1310: de dag la zag pa yod med kyi khyad par bsam pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1314: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK063(gu)003:1315: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK063(gu)003:1319: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK063(gu)003:1323: gang gis rtogs bya lta ba'i rang bzhin dang /
NK063(gu)003:1324: gang gis rtogs byed blo'i ngo bo dang /
NK063(gu)003:1325: des ji ltar rtogs pa'i tshul lo //
NK063(gu)003:1327: thams cad kyi rang bzhin ji ltar gnas pa de yin te /
NK063(gu)003:1329: chos kyi rang bzhin ji lta bu //
NK063(gu)003:1330: bdag gis yang dag rtogs bya ba //
NK063(gu)003:1333: thos bsam las byung ba'i shes rab kyi dbang po de yin te /
NK063(gu)003:1335: rgyu yi dkyil 'khor mthong bya'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:1336: thos bsam dam pa 'tshol bar byed //
NK063(gu)003:1339: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK063(gu)003:1340: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK063(gu)003:1344: de ltar ldan pas spyan tshol tshe //
NK063(gu)003:1345: gtan tshigs rnams kyis smal byas te //
NK063(gu)003:1346: nor ba'i shes rab dmigs bsal te //
NK063(gu)003:1347: ma nor dmigs nas bslang bar bya //
NK063(gu)003:1348: zhes pas gzhal bya gtan tshigs kyis rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1350: gzhi dang gtan tshigs grub pa'i don //
NK063(gu)003:1352: gang gzhal bya chos can dang /
NK063(gu)003:1353: gang gis 'jal byed gtan tshigs dang /
NK063(gu)003:1354: de ltar gzhal ba'i grub mtha'o //
NK063(gu)003:1356: blo tshad mas rtogs par byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1357: de la rigs kyi bye brag gsum las skabs 'dir
NK063(gu)003:1358: dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad yin
NK063(gu)003:1360: de yang dngos su brtag gzhi ni //
NK063(gu)003:1363: de yang 'das pa'i rang mtshan yul du ma gyur
NK063(gu)003:1364: cing 'khor ba'i rang mtshan der bden par gtan la
NK063(gu)003:1365: phab kyang de nyid 'khrul pa yin pa'i phyir gzhal
NK063(gu)003:1366: ba la dgos pa med par 'gyur ro zhe na
NK063(gu)003:1367: / de gnyis kyi rang mtshan gzhal bya ma yin no //
NK063(gu)003:1369: 'das par snang yang 'khor bar zhen pa'i snang zhen gnyis kyi tshogs pa de yin te /
NK063(gu)003:1371: zhen snang 'jal la skyon pa med //
NK063(gu)003:1374: tshul gsum tshang bas rtsod gzhi'i steng du dgag sgrub gnyis kyi byed las dang ldan pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1376: de phyir gtan tshigs las la brjod //
NK063(gu)003:1379: sgra mthun don spags kyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:1380: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs so //
NK063(gu)003:1382: gcig dang du bral gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK063(gu)003:1383: dmag tshogs dang nam mkha' ltar gcig dang du bral
NK063(gu)003:1384: yin pa'i phyir zhen snang der ma grub pa ste
NK063(gu)003:1386: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK063(gu)003:1387: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK063(gu)003:1389: rgyu'i theg pa pas de spangs nas bral bar 'dod pa las 'dir ma spangs pa'i phyir spags so //
NK063(gu)003:1391: snang tsam la blo 'khrul pa'i dbang gis der zhen pa ni kun rdzob dang /
NK063(gu)003:1392: de ma 'khrul pa de dang ldan pa ni don te /
NK063(gu)003:1394: yang dag sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su //
NK063(gu)003:1395: bdag dang bdag gir gzhan med de //
NK063(gu)003:1397: de yang cig shos kyis bden pa tha dad du
NK063(gu)003:1398: brtags te dgag sgrub byed pa las 'dir dbyer med
NK063(gu)003:1399: pa'i phyir de dang bral bas spags so //
NK063(gu)003:1401: bum pa'i dbyibs dang kha dog la sogs par byung
NK063(gu)003:1402: bas phyi yul gyi rnam pa rnams gcig tu ma
NK063(gu)003:1403: grub pa'i phyir yang dag par na chos kyi dbyings
NK063(gu)003:1404: yin te / rgyas pa'i nga gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)003:1405: 'byung ba chen po lnga rnams la //
NK063(gu)003:1406: rang bzhin med par gzhig bya'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:1407: gcig la'ang lnga lngar dbye bya ste //
NK063(gu)003:1408: yum gyi dbyings su thim par bya //
NK063(gu)003:1410: de yang cig shos 'byung ba bzhi la 'byung chung
NK063(gu)003:1411: bzhi bzhir phye nas tha dad du gtan la 'bebs
NK063(gu)003:1412: pa las / 'dir mtshon byed yum gyis mtshon bya
NK063(gu)003:1413: chos kyi dbyings su gcig par 'bebs pas 'phags so
NK063(gu)003:1415: sbrul snang la dpyad par thag khra rtogs pa ltar /
NK063(gu)003:1416: zhen byed nyon mongs rang mtshan la dpyad pas zhen pa spyi mtshan de bzhin nyid rtogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1418: nyon mongs rang dang spyir bstan pa //
NK063(gu)003:1419: mtshan nyid ma nor don rtogs na //
NK063(gu)003:1420: rnam par byang ba'i lam du 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:1422: de yang cig shos zhe sdang brnab sems spun dgu
NK063(gu)003:1423: la sogs rnams spyi mtshan mi rtag sdug bsngal stong
NK063(gu)003:1424: bdag med la sogs pas spong sbyong byed la /
NK063(gu)003:1425: 'dir rang mtshan spros bral du rtogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1426: mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK063(gu)003:1427: me long dang gtan tshigs ltar phyogs ris mi 'dra
NK063(gu)003:1428: ba med pa'i phyir ji ltar snang ba thams cad
NK063(gu)003:1431: nam mkha' bzung du med pa ltar //
NK063(gu)003:1432: snang srid thams cad de dang 'dra //
NK063(gu)003:1434: de yang cig shos dpe don tha dad du 'dod pa las /
NK063(gu)003:1435: 'dir thams cad chos nyid du gcig pa'i phyir dbyer med pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1441: rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK063(gu)003:1442: dang po rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK063(gu)003:1443: dngos po gnyis ka'i rgyu sems su gcig cing de'i rang bzhin stong par gcig pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1444: de ltar rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa las dngos po gnyis su snang ba'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:1445: ga bur nyid nad rkyen gyis sman dug gnyis su snang ba bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:1446: des na 'di ni rim gyis pa la ltos te sems stong pa shes byed kyi rtags so //
NK063(gu)003:1448: sems nyid de ltar mtshon byed yi ger ma 'gags pa yin te /
NK063(gu)003:1449: de ltar mtshon pa'i yi ge 'dus pa las byung ba'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:1450: ri bong can la zla ba'i sgras brjod pa bzhin /
NK063(gu)003:1451: des na 'di ni snang ldog gi rtags so //
NK063(gu)003:1453: gong ma snang stong gnyis dngos su rtogs pa las byung ba yin te /
NK063(gu)003:1454: de med na 'di mi 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:1455: sa bon med na myu gu med pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:1456: des na dbyer med kyi rtags so //
NK063(gu)003:1457: mngon sum pa ni bzhi las /
NK063(gu)003:1458: 'dir rang rig pa'i mngon sum de sems dang sems
NK063(gu)003:1459: las byung ba'i chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ji
NK063(gu)003:1460: ltar yin pa'i don phyin ci ma log par rtogs
NK063(gu)003:1461: pa ni rtags la brten pa ma yin zhing de
NK063(gu)003:1462: dang mi 'gal bar nges pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1464: mngon sum rtogs pa rtog pa'i mchog /
NK063(gu)003:1465: rang rig ye shes tshogs gcig pu //
NK063(gu)003:1468: phyi snod 'byung ba lnga nang bcud phung po lnga
NK063(gu)003:1469: rgyud rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar
NK063(gu)003:1470: dag par rtogs shing goms pas de dag nyid du
NK063(gu)003:1471: gyur pa'i phyir zad par gyi skye mched bzhin no
NK063(gu)003:1473: chos thams cad kun rdzob sgyu ma dang don dam spros bral te /
NK063(gu)003:1475: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK063(gu)003:1476: zhes pas snang ba sna tshogs pa ni don dam
NK063(gu)003:1477: stong pa'i ngo bo nyid las snang ba'i phyir rgyu
NK063(gu)003:1478: gzhan la ltos med yin zhing de nyid kyis stong
NK063(gu)003:1479: pa dang rang bcas su 'brel ba snang ba nyid
NK063(gu)003:1480: kyi rgyu las gzhan ltos med yin pa'i phyiir ro
NK063(gu)003:1482: de dag ngo bo nyid rgyur gnas //
NK063(gu)003:1484: gzhal bya zhen snang nyid la gong gi rtags rnams
NK063(gu)003:1485: kyis gzhal bas 'khrul pa ye shes su dbang sgyur
NK063(gu)003:1486: ba ni chos nyid la chos nyid spyod pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)003:1487: rang gi longs spyod rang gis spyod pa bzhin no
NK063(gu)003:1488: // tha ma ni le'u tha ma las /
NK063(gu)003:1489: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK063(gu)003:1490: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK063(gu)003:1492: ngo bo nyid du grub cing gnas pa yin te /
NK063(gu)003:1493: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i tshe de ltar yin pa dang skad cig kyang ma bral zhing /
NK063(gu)003:1494: de ltar nges pa'i tshe de gnyis gzhan dang gzhan
NK063(gu)003:1495: du ma grub pa'i phyir sbrul snang dang thag khra
NK063(gu)003:1496: bzhin no // tha ma grub pa'i mtha' ni /
NK063(gu)003:1497: gtan tshigs de dag gis gzhal bas gzhan snang de
NK063(gu)003:1498: bzhin nyid du gtan la phebs pa ni bsgrub bya
NK063(gu)003:1499: yin la / des mthar thug gi 'bras bu grub mtha' yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:1501: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK063(gu)003:1502: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /
NK063(gu)003:1511: 'dir de dag re re yang chos lnga lnga dang ldan par ston te /
NK063(gu)003:1512: gang nyams su len pa lam gyi ngo bo ni dmigs pa yul du byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1515: shin tu mi dmigs dbyings su sgom //
NK063(gu)003:1517: gnyis pa bying rgod dang bral ba'i rang rig sgyu ma ltar gsal ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:1519: thams cad sgyu ma mig yor tshul //
NK063(gu)003:1521: gsum pa phyag rgya bzhi ldan gyi sku snang la rang bzhin med par gsal ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:1522: sku gcig rdo rje dril 'bar sgom //
NK063(gu)003:1524: bzhi pa ni rtog pa mtha' dag lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:1525: spyod yul kun tu ma d+ha la //
NK063(gu)003:1527: tha ma ni rnal 'byor pho mo yo byad du
NK063(gu)003:1528: ma la brten nas lha du ma'i dngos grub don
NK063(gu)003:1531: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa grub //
NK063(gu)003:1533: der nges pa'i tshig sgra bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1534: mnyam bzhag la sems rtse gcig tu gnas pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:1535: gnyis pa sgyu ma ltar snang ba la rtse gcig pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:1536: gsum pa rtsa ba'i lha dang gcig du gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1537: bzhi pa rtsa ba'i lha rags pa du mar gsal ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:1538: tha ma rnal 'byor pa dang lha dang yo byad du ma tshogs dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1539: lam de nyams su blangs pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1540: dang po dngos po la der zhen gyi rtog pa dag cing don dam rtogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1541: gnyis pa'i stong pa phyogs gcig la zhen pa grol zhing sems can gyi don mi 'gog pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1542: gsum pa rtog pa gnas gyur zhing spros pa'i rgyur gyur pa /
NK063(gu)003:1543: bzhi pa lhar zhen pa las grol zhing rtog pa mtha' dag las log pa /
NK063(gu)003:1544: tha ma'i si ti gnyis ka la dbang sgyur ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1545: de dag gi rnam grangs ni /
NK063(gu)003:1546: dang po dbu ma'i phyogs gcig /
NK063(gu)003:1551: rten 'brel dngos po sgyu ma gsum 'khrul la /
NK063(gu)003:1552: thabs ye shes phyag rgya sgyu ma gsum ni ma 'khrul pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1553: gsum pa'i zhi ba dang khro bo phyag rgya gcig pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1554: bzhi pa'i zhi khro gnyis char la dkyil 'khor dang
NK063(gu)003:1555: tshom bu dang zhal phyag dang rnam grangs spros pa'o
NK063(gu)003:1556: // tha ma ni zhi khro gnyis re re la yang tshom bu gcig pa gsum pa lnga pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1558: dang po don dam mngon du byed pas rtog pa las grol /
NK063(gu)003:1559: gnyis pa kun rdzob ye shes su gsal bas 'dzin pa las grol /
NK063(gu)003:1560: gsum pa sku dang ye shes su gsal bas brtan pa thob //
NK063(gu)003:1561: bzhi pa snang ba phyag rgyar gsal ba la brtan pa rgya chen 'grub /
NK063(gu)003:1562: tha ma zag med la dngos su sbyor nus pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1564: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ste /
NK063(gu)003:1566: tshe la dbang dang phyag rgya che //
NK063(gu)003:1571: gsang ba'i yo byad lnga ldan pas //
NK063(gu)003:1572: brtson pas tshul bzhin rab bsgrubs na //
NK063(gu)003:1573: rdo rje'i lus dang rnam smin du //
NK063(gu)003:1577: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK063(gu)003:1578: 'di dag re re la yang bzhin bzhi dang ldan te /
NK063(gu)003:1579: gang gi rig sa 'dzin pa rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK063(gu)003:1580: lus rgyas bsgribs shing yid lha'i skur smin pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1581: gnyis pa ni lhag ma'i lus dang bcas nas 'bras bu la sbyor ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1582: de gnyis char sprul ba'i sku'o //
NK063(gu)003:1583: gsum pa ni bsgom bya mngon du gyur pas lha'i rang mtshan 'dzin pa longs sku'o //
NK063(gu)003:1584: bzhi pa ni lam mthar phyin pas spros pa dang bral ba'i phyir chos kyi sku'o //
NK063(gu)003:1585: der nges pa'i sgra don ni /
NK063(gu)003:1586: sems lha'i rnam par smin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1587: gnyis pa ni skye 'jig med pa rdo rje'i lus su gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1588: gsum pa ni mtshan dpe yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1589: tha ma ni sku lnga'i dgongs pa 'grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1590: dgongs pa'i khyad par ni zag med kyi shes rab kyis phyag rgya stong gi dkyil 'khor gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1591: gnyis pa chos nyid rang mtshan mthong zhing nyi khri bzhi stong du gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1592: gsum pa mthong ba'i don la mnyam par bzhag ste mi g.yo ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1593: tha ma na mnyam bzhag gi tshe sangs rgyas dang
NK063(gu)003:1594: khyad par med cing rjes thob bag la nyal dang
NK063(gu)003:1595: bcas pa'o // ji ltar bzhugs pa'i cha lugs ni /
NK063(gu)003:1596: gong ma gnyis sngon gang yin pa de mi dang lha dang /
NK063(gu)003:1599: tha ma gdul bya'i dbang gis ma nges par ston no //
NK063(gu)003:1600: don gnyis pa mthar chags pa ni lam gyi rim
NK063(gu)003:1601: pa dgu po 'di dag la mo tshod gang dang
NK063(gu)003:1602: mthun zhes rgyu'i theg pa pa dang gung sbyor ba
NK063(gu)003:1604: lam la bgrod tshul tha dad pa tsam las thun
NK063(gu)003:1605: min gyi khyad par med par 'gyur zhing gzhan yang
NK063(gu)003:1606: 'dir sems skye ba'i skye sar bshad pa dang 'gal
NK063(gu)003:1607: lo // rdo rje theg pa na babs su 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1609: rgyu 'bras khyad par lhun gyis grub //
NK063(gu)003:1611: thod rgal ba la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:1612: de 'byung ba'i rgyu khyad par gyi chos ni stong
NK063(gu)003:1613: snying ltar gnyis med bsgom mi nus shing rnam smin
NK063(gu)003:1614: ltar nang rigs kyi blo chung zhing lam nges pa
NK063(gu)003:1616: lhun grub ltar dor rgyu med pa nas mi 'byung ste /
NK063(gu)003:1617: gnyis med bsgom nus shing lam nges pa can min la /
NK063(gu)003:1618: lam dor rgyu yod cing nang rigs kyi blo che ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1620: zag bcas gcig spros tshogs gsum dang //
NK063(gu)003:1621: de bral tshe dbang rgya chen nas //
NK063(gu)003:1624: zag bcas gsum po tshe dbang yan chad ci rigs dang /
NK063(gu)003:1626: rgya dor cig car mthar 'gro ba //
NK063(gu)003:1629: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sa //
NK063(gu)003:1630: zhes rgya chen ni lhun grub las dor rgyu med de sangs rgyas kyi sa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1632: phyag rgya gcig pa nas phyag rgya gcig pa'i bar bskyed rim zhi khro gnyis su bstan la /
NK063(gu)003:1633: de las gzhan pa'i lam rnams ni de gnyis kyi chos dang bral ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1634: don tha ma la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:1635: zag pa'i mtshan nyid ni tha mal gyi 'dzin shes bag chags dang bcas pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1637: de dag 'jig rten pa la yod na 'dzin pa'i phyir zag par 'gyur la /
NK063(gu)003:1640: rang dbang med par 'dor pa lus kyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:1641: bde mi bder snang ba khams kyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:1642: las kyi stobs kyis rang dbang med pa'i lus len pa skye gnas kyi'o //
NK063(gu)003:1643: gang la yod med kyi khyad par ni gong gi mtshan nyid dang mi ldan te /
NK063(gu)003:1644: tshogs sgrub man chad zag bcas la rnam smin yan chad zag med do //
NK063(gu)003:1645: de yang kha cig rnam smin la zag bcas yin yang zag med du 'debs zer ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:1646: kha cig gtso bo skye gnas len pas zag med yin zer ba la /
NK063(gu)003:1648: sa phyogs na shing gi bye brag yod pas shing yod du 'gyur ba ltar /
NK063(gu)003:1649: rnam smin la lus khams kyi zag pa rtags su
NK063(gu)003:1650: bkod nas zag bcas su bsgrub pa la'ang gnod pa
NK063(gu)003:1651: can te / khams bde mi bde dang lus dor ba tsam gyis der gyur na /
NK063(gu)003:1652: sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa'i sku yang der 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)003:1653: de gnyis yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:1654: des na rnam smin lus la rang dbang yod par 'dod pa yod pa gang na med do //
NK063(gu)003:1655: gnyis pa cig car ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:1657: de nyid kho na cig car ba //
NK063(gu)003:1659: 'di yang gong ltar mtshan nyid gsum las /
NK063(gu)003:1661: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs dbyer med du rtogs
NK063(gu)003:1662: pas gzhal bya dang gtan tshigs la sogs pa'i tha
NK063(gu)003:1665: chos dang chos can kun bral bar //
NK063(gu)003:1667: mi phyed rdo rje thugs mchog go //
NK063(gu)003:1670: mi rtog pa bsgom pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:1671: phyag rgya bsgom pa'i cig car ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1674: sgom pa'i rim pa bslab bya bral //
NK063(gu)003:1675: ma bcos ji bzhin ngang bzhag dang //
NK063(gu)003:1677: mi gnas gnas la gnas par sgom //
NK063(gu)003:1680: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK063(gu)003:1683: lhun gyis bsgoms zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:1685: theg le chen po nyag gcig la //
NK063(gu)003:1686: sgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK063(gu)003:1690: nyi zla gza' skar ji bzhin du //
NK063(gu)003:1691: rgya mtsho dwangs par gsal ba bzhin //
NK063(gu)003:1693: snying po brjod pas 'khor lo rdzogs //
NK063(gu)003:1695: tha ma ni rig 'dzin bzhi'i char gtogs pa'i ye shes gcig la grub pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1698: skabs kyis rdzogs pa chen por brjod //
NK063(gu)003:1699: ces pas 'dir kha cig cig car ba la sems lnga rim par skye'am mi skye /
NK063(gu)003:1700: dang po ltar na cig car ba ma yin par 'gyur la /
NK063(gu)003:1701: gnyis pa ltar na cig car ba de lam gyi ngo bo min par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)003:1702: sems lnga mi skye ba'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)003:1703: skye bas skyon phyi ma med la /
NK063(gu)003:1704: dus myur bas skyon dang po'ang med de /
NK063(gu)003:1705: sho mang lnga brtsegs la khab brdeg pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:1706: rim gyis pa ni rdo shing lnga 'bugs pa lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)003:1707: le'u gang nas ston pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1708: rang bzhin gyi snang ba ston pa rnams dang mthun no //
NK063(gu)003:1709: don gnyis pa thabs kyi lam la'ang gnyis te /
NK063(gu)003:1713: gdams ngag gis 'ching ba la spyad pas mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'grub byed du gyur pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1715: gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo //
NK063(gu)003:1717: rim gyis pa steng sgo dang /
NK063(gu)003:1720: sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa ni rgyu mtshan nyid
NK063(gu)003:1721: dang ldan pa gcig la phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang
NK063(gu)003:1722: yongs su rdzogs par zhus nas 'khor gsum yongs su
NK063(gu)003:1723: dag pa byas te gnas dben par stan bde ba
NK063(gu)003:1724: la 'dug ste snang mdzad kyi chos bdun baca'o //
NK063(gu)003:1725: rang lus la rtsa dang 'khor lo'i gnas tshul ni /
NK063(gu)003:1727: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK063(gu)003:1728: zhes pas dngos gzhi'i 'khor lo bzhi dang cha rkyen gyi 'khor lo gnyis so //
NK063(gu)003:1730: bcu gsum gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK063(gu)003:1731: bde ba'i thig le mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK063(gu)003:1732: zhes pas spyi gtsug bde chen gyi tsakra na rtsa sum cu rtsa gnyis gnas /
NK063(gu)003:1733: de'i dbus na byang chub sems kyi yi ge ham
NK063(gu)003:1734: dkar po mgo thur du bstan pa gcig gnas so
NK063(gu)003:1736: lnga gnyis drug gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK063(gu)003:1737: zhes pas mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo na rtsa bcu drug gnas /
NK063(gu)003:1738: de'i dbus na 'dod yon gyi yi ge gcig gnas /
NK063(gu)003:1740: gang la yod pa gnas pa brgyad du shes //
NK063(gu)003:1742: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab brgyad gnas /
NK063(gu)003:1743: de'i dbus na kun gzhi kun pho'i yi ge h+aum mthing kha gcig gnas so //
NK063(gu)003:1745: bcu drug bcu bzhi'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK063(gu)003:1746: zhes pas lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi gnas /
NK063(gu)003:1747: de'i dbus na kun mo'i yi ge am mthing kha gcig gnas so //
NK063(gu)003:1748: lte ba'i 'og nas sor bzhi bcal ba'i sa na
NK063(gu)003:1749: don dam me'i 'khor lo zhes bya ba dbyibs gru
NK063(gu)003:1750: gsum ram gyis mtshan pa gcig gnas /
NK063(gu)003:1751: sba kha na sgrom mdo rlung gi tsakra zhes bya
NK063(gu)003:1752: ba dbyibs zla gam yi ge yam gis mtshan pa
NK063(gu)003:1753: gcig gnas so // kun dar ma gdugs kyi yu ba'i tshul du dbus na yar gnas /
NK063(gu)003:1754: tsakra rnams gdugs phub pa'i tshul du gnas /
NK063(gu)003:1755: ro rkyang gnyis gdugs rten pa'i tshul du g.yas g.yon na gnas so //
NK063(gu)003:1756: de lam pas ji ltar bsgom pa'i thabs ni /
NK063(gu)003:1757: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK063(gu)003:1758: bzho bas zhes gdams ngag ltar rngub dgang bskyil dbab
NK063(gu)003:1759: la sogs gtum mo 'bar 'dzag la brten nas bde
NK063(gu)003:1760: ba rim gyis bskyed pa'i phyir steng du rnam par
NK063(gu)003:1762: de ltar bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu ni dngos su rlung
NK063(gu)003:1763: sems la dbang thob pas 'og sgo nyams su blang
NK063(gu)003:1764: du rung zhing brgyud nas de'i 'bras bu dang thun
NK063(gu)003:1765: mong du'o // gnyis pa la'ang bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)003:1766: rigs dang mthun pa'i yum brtag cing dbang du bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:1768: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK063(gu)003:1769: dabye'am yang na mi dbye bar //
NK063(gu)003:1772: dgug dang zhes pa thabs kyis so //
NK063(gu)003:1773: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos dang ldan pa'i lhar bskyed cing brlab pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1775: gos rgyan mdzes pa zhes pa bklubs shing 'phur ba
NK063(gu)003:1776: dar gyi gos rat+na'i sil khrol gyi rgyan gyis mdzes
NK063(gu)003:1777: par byas te / bcu gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)003:1778: bsnyen pa dang ni zhes phyi nang gi khrus kyis
NK063(gu)003:1779: rgyud dag par byas nas dam dpog cing dbang bskur
NK063(gu)003:1780: ro // skye mched dang mkha' gsang brlab bo //
NK063(gu)003:1781: sgrub pa dang ni zhes pas /
NK063(gu)003:1782: dngos gzhi +aa li yab dang k+aa li yum gyis
NK063(gu)003:1783: snyoms par zhugs pa'i dgongs pa nyams su blang ba
NK063(gu)003:1785: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK063(gu)003:1788: sgrub pa chen po zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1790: sgrub pa nyi zla'i snying po de //
NK063(gu)003:1791: de la rdo rje lce yis blang //
NK063(gu)003:1792: ldog dang dgram ste de ltar ro //
NK063(gu)003:1793: de ltar nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK063(gu)003:1797: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:1800: thabs lam rgyu dang rim pa ni //
NK063(gu)003:1802: rlung 'gag las la goms pas ni //
NK063(gu)003:1803: shin tu bde ba 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK063(gu)003:1804: gsang dbang pad+ma ltar gyur na //
NK063(gu)003:1805: chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis su //
NK063(gu)003:1806: bcu dang gsum gyi rgyu 'bras rnams //
NK063(gu)003:1807: rdzogs phyir rim dang ldog shes na //
NK063(gu)003:1808: byin rlabs shugs kyis yang dag 'thob //
NK063(gu)003:1810: dkyil 'khor rdul snyed grangs med dang //
NK063(gu)003:1811: phun sum tshogs pa lhun grub rnams //
NK063(gu)003:1812: gsang dbang mchog gis 'byin byed pas //
NK063(gu)003:1813: thabs kyi lam la'ang 'bad par bya //
NK063(gu)003:1823: bco brgyad pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK063(gu)003:1826: phun sum tshogs pa lhun grub rnams //
NK063(gu)003:1827: gsang dbang mchog gis 'byin par byed //
NK063(gu)003:1828: ces pas cig shos kyis kyang 'bras bu la sbyor la /
NK063(gu)003:1830: thos bsam sgom pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK063(gu)003:1831: rang byung kun ngam 'grub byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1832: zhes pas grol lam gyis kyang 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i phyir tha dad ces 'dod kyang /
NK063(gu)003:1833: 'dir grol lam gyi sngon du dbang 'gro zhing /
NK063(gu)003:1834: dbang gi sngon du sems bskyed pa'i phyir 'brel ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:1835: de yang tshogs sgrub pa'i tshe tan gan la spyod pa ni thabs yin la /
NK063(gu)003:1836: de la lta bas zin dgos pa'i phyir dngos su 'brel ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1837: tha ma ni grol lam sngon du 'gro ba yin te /
NK063(gu)003:1838: dbang gi sngon du sems bskyed par nges shing cig shos kyi lam ma yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:1840: lam gyi shes rab sngon 'gro ba //
NK063(gu)003:1841: thabs la de nyid rim par bslab //
NK063(gu)003:1845: lam gyi yan lag rkyen bzhag pa //
NK063(gu)003:1846: rjes mthun spyod dang lha dbang dam //
NK063(gu)003:1847: sgrub dang mchod dang phrin las dang //
NK063(gu)003:1848: dkyil 'khor la sogs brgyad kyis rdzogs //
NK063(gu)003:1851: lta spyod dkyil 'kho dbang dam dang //
NK063(gu)003:1852: phrin las sgrub pa'i las rim gyis //
NK063(gu)003:1853: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye ba bya //
NK063(gu)003:1854: zhes pas bdun yang don gyi bcur gnas pa las /
NK063(gu)003:1855: 'di rnams re re yang thugs thigs las chos ma nges par bstan kyang /
NK063(gu)003:1856: 'dir nya ri ba'i gsung sgros kyis /
NK063(gu)003:1857: de dag gi dgos pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:1861: de dang mi ldan pa'am med pa'i skyon dang /
NK063(gu)003:1862: yon tan dang drug tu gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)003:1863: de las dang po lta ba la drug las /
NK063(gu)003:1866: gzhan pa'i lta dmigs bsal ba dang //
NK063(gu)003:1867: zhes pa gzhan sel ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:1869: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK063(gu)003:1870: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK063(gu)003:1872: mchog gi spyan rab thob bya'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:1873: zhes pas don du gnyer ba'i dgos pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:1875: chos nyid yang dag rtogs pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1877: chos kyi rang bzhin ji lta bu //
NK063(gu)003:1878: bdag gis yang dag rtogs bya ba //
NK063(gu)003:1880: las gang la spyad kyang mi 'ching ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:1882: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yis //
NK063(gu)003:1883: dug lnga dug gsum gnod mi 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:1885: sangs rgyas nyid 'thob pa'i dngos rgyur gyur pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1887: rang rig ye shes don rtogs na //
NK063(gu)003:1888: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung 'thob //
NK063(gu)003:1891: don dam du ni dkor bdun no //
NK063(gu)003:1893: rigs pa sgyu ma nyid ni med pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1894: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK063(gu)003:1896: de gnyis tshig snga phyi yang don gcig pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:1897: tshig gis snga phyir byung mod kyang //
NK063(gu)003:1898: don gyis cig car rdzogs par sgom //
NK063(gu)003:1900: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK063(gu)003:1901: yang dag nyid du rab tu rtogs //
NK063(gu)003:1903: don dam cir yang snang ba ngo bo nyid du
NK063(gu)003:1904: grub pa la chos nyid de nges shing kun rdzob
NK063(gu)003:1906: lhun grub ye shes sgron ma nyid //
NK063(gu)003:1907: rang gzhan gsal ba spyan gyi mchog /
NK063(gu)003:1908: ngo bo de bzhin nyid du shes //
NK063(gu)003:1911: d+hi ti'i sgra las lnga pa zhes bya la de
NK063(gu)003:1912: ni bden don mthong bas gdengs su gyur pa ste
NK063(gu)003:1914: yul med gsal phyir lta zhes bshad //
NK063(gu)003:1917: lta dang blta bar bya med de //
NK063(gu)003:1918: ye shes sgron ma bsgreng bas ni //
NK063(gu)003:1919: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams ma lus mthong //
NK063(gu)003:1922: gol sgrib gdar sha bcad de dang /
NK063(gu)003:1923: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste dang /
NK063(gu)003:1924: rnam grangs rnam par phye nas dmigs gzung ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1931: dang po la'ang sgrib pa'i mtshan nyid ni mthong bar bya ba las gegs su gyur pa yin cing /
NK063(gu)003:1932: des bgrod bya las phyin ci log tu gyur pa ni gol ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:1934: ma rtogs pa rgyud drug dang /
NK063(gu)003:1935: log par rtogs pa rtag chad dang /
NK063(gu)003:1936: phyogs 'ga' tsam rtogs pa 'og ma ba rnams te /
NK063(gu)003:1937: de dag gis yod med du sgro btags shing skur ba btab pa ni gol sgrib kyi ngo bo'o //
NK063(gu)003:1940: gtan tshigs thun mong yin min pa //
NK063(gu)003:1941: rgyud las grags pas rkyen byas te //
NK063(gu)003:1942: ri rgyal lta bu mthong ba yi //
NK063(gu)003:1943: zhes pas bar pa gtan tshigs kyis gtan la dbab
NK063(gu)003:1944: pa dngos te rgyu shes pa'i skabs su bstan zin
NK063(gu)003:1945: no // tha ma rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba ni gnyis las /
NK063(gu)003:1946: ming gi rnam grangs ni tshogs brgyad de /
NK063(gu)003:1948: tshogs brgyad po 'di rten gzugs can gyis yul tha
NK063(gu)003:1949: dad la sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i phyir gyi rnam grangs
NK063(gu)003:1950: yin zer ba ni ma yin te /
NK063(gu)003:1952: dbang po drug gi char snang yang //
NK063(gu)003:1953: spyan la mchog tu brjod pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:1954: shes rab yul du dbyer med pas //
NK063(gu)003:1955: mngon sum rtogs pa rtogs pa'i mchog /
NK063(gu)003:1956: rang rig ye shes tshogs gcig pu //
NK063(gu)003:1959: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal stong gzugs //
NK063(gu)003:1960: khyab gsal rang bzhin go ba'i sgra //
NK063(gu)003:1961: dang bas tshim byed chos kyi dri //
NK063(gu)003:1962: don bcud nyams su myong ba'i ro //
NK063(gu)003:1963: yang dag don la reg pa nyid //
NK063(gu)003:1964: chos khams sna tshogs kun mkhyen pas //
NK063(gu)003:1965: rang rig rgyal por rang snang ngo //
NK063(gu)003:1967: don gyi rnam grangs la yang gnyis las //
NK063(gu)003:1968: nyams su len byed lam gyi rim pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:1970: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK063(gu)003:1971: rang rig ye shes snying rjes gzigs //
NK063(gu)003:1972: phyag rgya gcig sku 'bras bur lta //
NK063(gu)003:1973: thams cad gsal ba'i lta ba dang //
