NK063(gu)003:1974: bar chad med dang tshogs chen mthong //
NK063(gu)003:1975: thams cad mnyam nyid mi g.yo ba //
NK063(gu)003:1976: ye shes kun mkhyen lta ba dgu //
NK063(gu)003:1977: zhes pas khyab bya lam de dag la khyab byed
NK063(gu)003:1978: lta bas khyab pas lam gyi rim pa'i lta grangs
NK063(gu)003:1979: zhes bya'o // gnyis pa nyams su blang bya rgyud
NK063(gu)003:1980: don rnams la yang khyab byed lta bas khyab phyir
NK063(gu)003:1981: rgyud don gyi lta grangs zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)003:1982: lta ba ma rtogs pa'i skyon ni gnyis te /
NK063(gu)003:1983: dge ba la skur ba min yang ma rtogs na
NK063(gu)003:1984: gnas skabs su dge ba spyad kyang 'khor ba las
NK063(gu)003:1985: mi grol te / nga gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)003:1986: thabs la mkhas pas ma zin na //
NK063(gu)003:1987: lam gyi dge spyad rtag spyad kyang //
NK063(gu)003:1988: mtho ris lha dang mir skye yi //
NK063(gu)003:1989: skye shi med pa'i sa mi 'thob //
NK063(gu)003:1991: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yang 'khor ba'i gnas su mthong ba'i skyon no //
NK063(gu)003:1992: rtogs pa'i yon tan la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:1993: ngan song gi gnas nyid 'og min gyi zhing du rtogs pa ni //
NK063(gu)003:1994: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pa na //
NK063(gu)003:1995: ngan song gnas nyid 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK063(gu)003:1997: ci la spyad kyang mi 'ching ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:1998: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yis //
NK063(gu)003:1999: dug lnga dug gsum gnod mi 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2001: slar yang mi 'khrul te sangs rgyas nyid 'thob pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2002: gnas lugs bden don rtogs pas 'khor ba'i skyon spangs
NK063(gu)003:2003: pa min pa'i phyir mi gos la sangs rgyas kyi
NK063(gu)003:2004: che ba'i yon tan thob pa min pa'i phyir mi
NK063(gu)003:2005: nyams te / rgyas pa'i nyer gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)003:2006: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'di //
NK063(gu)003:2007: chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK063(gu)003:2008: dang po don rtogs mtha' mi gtong //
NK063(gu)003:2009: spyod yul kun tu tshad dpag med //
NK063(gu)003:2026: re gsum pa rnams nas so //
NK063(gu)003:2027: gnyis pa spyod pa la drug las /
NK063(gu)003:2030: bdag dang gzhan gyi don gyi phyir //
NK063(gu)003:2031: bri sogs mi gos goms par byed //
NK063(gu)003:2032: ces pas sgo gsum tha mal las ldog nas lta sgom stobs su gyur pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2035: rjes mthun spyod pa gzhung bzhin spyad //
NK063(gu)003:2038: lam pa'i sgo gsum gyi bya bar gyur ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:2040: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK063(gu)003:2041: gang na'ang mi gnas mi dmigs pas //
NK063(gu)003:2044: tsar+ya zhes pa'i sgras spyod pa zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)003:2045: de ni spyad bya la spyod pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:2047: sgo gsum las phyir nges tshig 'grub //
NK063(gu)003:2051: zhor la dus nam gyi tshe spyad pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2053: kun kyang mnyam las langs tshe'o //
NK063(gu)003:2057: de yang bdag gzhan don du'o //
NK063(gu)003:2061: dkyil 'khor rol pa'i tshul spyod la //
NK063(gu)003:2062: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa bdag gi don //
NK063(gu)003:2064: gzhan don gyi spyod pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2065: smin pas phrin las rdzogs byed pa //
NK063(gu)003:2070: thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2073: cig car ba blang dor dang bral ba rmad du byung ba'i spyod pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2075: zag bcas kyi lam du dang /
NK063(gu)003:2076: bar chad med pa'i lam du dang /
NK063(gu)003:2077: zag med kyi lam du ji ltar spyad pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2080: thos bsam bcu spyod ched du gnyer //
NK063(gu)003:2083: gzhan phyir so so'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK063(gu)003:2084: don ni ci smos dang po bcu //
NK063(gu)003:2085: gzhan la ston cing bkri bar bya //
NK063(gu)003:2086: zhes pas dad brtson gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:2088: bya ba med las bya med bya //
NK063(gu)003:2089: zhes pas shes rab dang mthun pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:2090: thabs kyis pha rol phyin spyod la //
NK063(gu)003:2091: zhes pas thabs dang mthun pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:2093: chos spyod bcu yi cha gcig la gnas pa //
NK063(gu)003:2095: phyogs gcig spyod la gang gnas pa //
NK063(gu)003:2098: rgyu 'bras mtshams sbyor bar skabs kun //
NK063(gu)003:2099: chos spyod dgu yi spros pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:2100: rgyud la ldan yang blang bya min //
NK063(gu)003:2101: mtshan ma'i g.yo ba yin phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:2102: zhes pas phyogs gcig pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:2103: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde la //
NK063(gu)003:2104: ma nyams blo dang ldan pa yis //
NK063(gu)003:2105: mnyam las langs tshe spyod pa ni //
NK063(gu)003:2107: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK063(gu)003:2108: rnam smin +amo du shes par bya //
NK063(gu)003:2109: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du sgom //
NK063(gu)003:2110: yang na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor sgom //
NK063(gu)003:2111: zhes pas spros bcas kyi spyod pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2112: bar chad med pa'i lam du ni /
NK063(gu)003:2114: gos rgyan bza' btung glu dang tshig /
NK063(gu)003:2115: bro gar tshogs kyi sprin phung las //
NK063(gu)003:2116: h+aum du shes pas rab spyad na //
NK063(gu)003:2120: rnam smin tshe dbang gi spyod pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2122: kun tu 'gro ba bdag po'i don //
NK063(gu)003:2123: zhes pas rang don kun tu 'gro'i dri ma sbyong zhing lam gong ma la sbyor ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:2124: phyag rgya chen po'i ni shes rab gsum gyis lhan
NK063(gu)003:2125: cig gnas pa'i dri ma sbyong zhing gong ma la'o
NK063(gu)003:2126: // lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi spyod pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2128: nyid phyir rdo rje 'dzin rdzogs la //
NK063(gu)003:2129: skad cig dus kyis bslab rdzogs na /
NK063(gu)003:2130: bag la nyal ba'i sgrib pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:2131: bcom ldan 'das par gyur pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:2132: shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyong zhing sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2133: cig car ba blang dor dang bral ba rmad du byung ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2134: rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)003:2135: rnal 'byor chen po'i spyod pa ni //
NK063(gu)003:2136: thams cad kun la dbyer med spyod //
NK063(gu)003:2139: spyod pa ci la'ang thogs med spyod //
NK063(gu)003:2141: gnyis pa thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2143: sems can rtog pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:2144: gtso ru dang du blang bar bya //
NK063(gu)003:2147: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK063(gu)003:2149: zhing gyur mchog dang zhes pa la sogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2152: khyad par gyi spyod pa dang mi ldan na mthar thug gi 'bras bu mi thob ste /
NK063(gu)003:2153: khyad par med na mthar phyin med //
NK063(gu)003:2156: tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing sgrib gnyis 'byang bar 'gyur ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:2164: bcu dgu pa rnams nas so //
NK063(gu)003:2165: gsum pa bkod pa dkyil 'khor la drug las /
NK063(gu)003:2168: dkyil 'khor dgos pa'i dus lnga dang //
NK063(gu)003:2169: zhes pas dbang sgrub mchod phrin rab gnas rnams gson don no //
NK063(gu)003:2170: ro bsreg gnas sbyang gnyis gshin don no //
NK063(gu)003:2171: de dag gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs rnams sel zhing don rnams bsgrub pa'i ched do //
NK063(gu)003:2174: gnas skabs bdun du snying po len //
NK063(gu)003:2175: bkod pa gang rdzogs de ngo bo //
NK063(gu)003:2178: ngo bo chos rnams thams cad de //
NK063(gu)003:2179: bden pa gnyis kyi mtshan ma can //
NK063(gu)003:2180: don dam spros pa med pa las //
NK063(gu)003:2181: kun rdzob gtso 'khor de nyid do //
NK063(gu)003:2184: ma d+ha la'i sgras dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)003:2185: de ni gang gtso bo la 'khor gyis bskor ba'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:2187: bdun gyi gtso snying gang gang la //
NK063(gu)003:2188: de yi 'khor ldan nges pa'i tshig /
NK063(gu)003:2191: nges tshig dkyil ni gtso bo ste //
NK063(gu)003:2192: 'khor ni de yi sprul pa ste //
NK063(gu)003:2197: dkyil 'khor dgos pa'i dus lnga dang //
NK063(gu)003:2202: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dang //
NK063(gu)003:2204: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK063(gu)003:2208: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:2210: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:2212: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)003:2215: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)003:2217: rang bzhin don dam gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK063(gu)003:2218: rgyas pa'i don gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)003:2219: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa //
NK063(gu)003:2220: snang grags bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK063(gu)003:2221: phyi dang nang gi rnam pa dag /
NK063(gu)003:2222: de bzhin dbyings kyi ngang du thim //
NK063(gu)003:2225: phyi nang snod bcud bdag rnams la //
NK063(gu)003:2226: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ye nas gnas //
NK063(gu)003:2230: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK063(gu)003:2231: chos dbyings dag dang dbyer med pas //
NK063(gu)003:2232: mnyam par sbyor zhing dag pa yi //
NK063(gu)003:2236: sangs rgyas kun gyi byang chub sems //
NK063(gu)003:2237: bla na med pa rtogs gyur pa //
NK063(gu)003:2238: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i ye shes gang //
NK063(gu)003:2239: de ni dkyil 'khor snying por gsungs //
NK063(gu)003:2243: bzhugs pa gtso dang 'khor gyi tshul //
NK063(gu)003:2245: 'di rgyas par 'bras bu'i skabs su ston /
NK063(gu)003:2246: 'dir dkyil 'khor gyi rnam grangs tsam du 'chad kyi lam gyi cha rkyen ma yin no //
NK063(gu)003:2248: don dam pa'i gzugs brnyan rtog pa kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du byung ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:2249: rnam rtog phra rags kyis lha yab yum du mtshon pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK063(gu)003:2250: de gnyis char yang 'og min na bzhugs pa dang 'di ltar gsal ba gnyis 'dra ba'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:2251: rgyas pa'i don bzhi pa las /
NK063(gu)003:2252: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK063(gu)003:2253: chen po rags pa thabs su rtogs //
NK063(gu)003:2254: mtshan nyid 'dzin pa shes rab ste //
NK063(gu)003:2255: gnyis med 'brel pas thabs chen yin //
NK063(gu)003:2258: dkyil 'khor gyi las kyis lhag pa ste sa la sogs pa la phyag rgyar bzhengs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2260: yang na sa gzhi rab mnyam la //
NK063(gu)003:2263: gser dngul lugs dang dung rdo 'bur /
NK063(gu)003:2264: rwa shing bzhog dang gyang ras ris //
NK063(gu)003:2265: sa myag lder dang rdul tshon bcas //
NK063(gu)003:2267: de la yang ngo bo rnam grangs ni sku gsung thugs gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:2268: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK063(gu)003:2269: ces pas gong gi dgos pa dang 'brel ba'i phyir gnas kyi rnam grangs lnga'am bdun no //
NK063(gu)003:2271: gang bsgom bya'i don la rtse gcig tu gnas pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2276: nyid kyi thugs la thim byas te //
NK063(gu)003:2277: yang dag chos sku'i phyag rgya che //
NK063(gu)003:2279: yang mtshan bcas ni lhag pa ting dkyil lo //
NK063(gu)003:2281: ting nge'i las lhag pa ste zhi khro gnyis so //
NK063(gu)003:2282: de re re yang sku'i ni 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas la sogs pa /
NK063(gu)003:2283: de bzhin ba cu gcig pa'i 'bar ba'i rgyal po rtsibs bzhi pa nor te /
NK063(gu)003:2284: 'khor lo rgyal po rgyal mo dang la sogs pa
NK063(gu)003:2285: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad la sogs pa'o
NK063(gu)003:2286: // gsung gi ni gcig pa'i sngags nor te gcig pa'i sngags /
NK063(gu)003:2287: bzhi pa'i yi ge nor te h+aum ha he phata la sogs sa bon no //
NK063(gu)003:2288: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor te mthing kha dkar po ser
NK063(gu)003:2289: le brgan nor te smug nag sngo nag ser nag
NK063(gu)003:2291: rdo rjee 'khor lo la sogs phyag mtshan nor gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)003:2292: stong gi 'jig rten la sogs so //
NK063(gu)003:2293: lha dang lha 'dra bar sgom zhes pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2296: de yang brten pa bde ba ni dkyil yin te /
NK063(gu)003:2303: gsang ba'i dbang po pad+mara ldan gyur na //
NK063(gu)003:2304: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor rnam pa gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:2306: de'i rten rtsa rnams 'khor yin pa'i phyir phyi dang nang dang gsang ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:2307: bzhi brgyad shi ra ma d+ha la //
NK063(gu)003:2310: zab phyir byang sems dkyil 'khor ni //
NK063(gu)003:2311: rten dang brten can tha snyad gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:2312: dbye ba phyi nang mthar thug 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2315: rigs gang la de'i 'khor gyis bskor ba 'di dkyil 'khor dang gcig pa dgag pa'i dbye ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:2316: de la'ang zhi khro gnyis so //
NK063(gu)003:2317: de re re'ang tshom bu gcig pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2318: rigs kyi rigs te la sogs bco brgyad dang /
NK063(gu)003:2319: de bzhin khro bo la yang /
NK063(gu)003:2320: dang por lnga bcu brgyad bsgoms nas //
NK063(gu)003:2323: de bzhin rigs dang rdo rje'i rigs //
NK063(gu)003:2324: zhes pa la sogs pa bzhi bcu drug dang /
NK063(gu)003:2325: bdun cu rtsa brgyad gsal ba dang //
NK063(gu)003:2328: lnga yi la sogs bdun cu dang //
NK063(gu)003:2329: dgu bcu rtsa brgyad de bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:2331: de dag gi bye brag gi nges tshig ni bzhi las /
NK063(gu)003:2334: 'das pa rtag tu dkyil yin te //
NK063(gu)003:2341: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa dang lnga'i ni /
NK063(gu)003:2343: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil nyid de //
NK063(gu)003:2344: rigs bzhi'i lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK063(gu)003:2347: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK063(gu)003:2353: snying po thams cad dus su dkyil //
NK063(gu)003:2354: gang yang yan lag 'khor du gsungs //
NK063(gu)003:2356: nang gi ni thig le ste /
NK063(gu)003:2357: bco brgyad khams gsum snying po nyid //
NK063(gu)003:2358: de dag 'khor te bde ba'i khams //
NK063(gu)003:2360: gsang ba ni bde ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:2361: ye shes ji bzhin lha de bzhin /
NK063(gu)003:2366: de las ldog pa'i skyon can bzhi //
NK063(gu)003:2367: grangs kyi rjes su ma nges par /
NK063(gu)003:2368: zhes pas 'og gi yon tan las ldog pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2373: de ni rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rang bzhin gyi snang ba bstan pa'i le'u rnams kyis so //
NK063(gu)003:2385: bcu bdun pa rnams nas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:2386: bzhi pa dbang la drug las /
NK063(gu)003:2387: dgos pa ni sgrib pa 'joms shing nus pa 'jog pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2388: ngo bo ni gang thabs kyi yan lag gis thob par bya ba ste lnga las /
NK063(gu)003:2389: thob bya'i ngo bo dngos ni /
NK063(gu)003:2391: ngo bo nus phan gsang ba dang //
NK063(gu)003:2392: shes rab ye shes bde chen po //
NK063(gu)003:2396: khyad par rgyu rkyen lngar bshad do //
NK063(gu)003:2398: snod dang sbyar te bskur ba'i rim pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2400: dad dang brtson 'grus gsum ldan pas //
NK063(gu)003:2401: brtul zhugs gsum pa spyod pa la //
NK063(gu)003:2402: go rim bzhin du 'tshams par sbyin //
NK063(gu)003:2405: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK063(gu)003:2406: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK063(gu)003:2407: rim pa bzhin du bskur bar bya //
NK063(gu)003:2414: gang du bskur zhing bstim pa'i gnas /
NK063(gu)003:2417: thob pa'i tshad dam dpe ni /
NK063(gu)003:2419: rgyal po phrug gu drug 'gyur zhing //
NK063(gu)003:2422: a b+hi shiny+tsa'am she ka'i sgras dbang zhes bya la
NK063(gu)003:2423: de ni mngon par gtor ba'am yon tan thob pa'i
NK063(gu)003:2424: phyir ro // rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)003:2428: dus ni rnam pa gsum du ste /
NK063(gu)003:2429: phyi nang dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum //
NK063(gu)003:2430: bskyed pa'i rim la slob pa'i dus //
NK063(gu)003:2431: rdzogs rim gdams ngag sbyor dus su //
NK063(gu)003:2436: dkyil 'khor las kyi rjes zhugs pas //
NK063(gu)003:2437: snod rim sbyar ba'i las rdzogs bya //
NK063(gu)003:2439: lam gyi rim pa'i sgo nas dang /
NK063(gu)003:2441: mos pa tha dad pa'i dbye ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:2443: zag bcas kyi lam du dbang gsum gyi nus pa tsam 'jog pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:2444: bar chad med pa'i lam du phal cher 'jog /
NK063(gu)003:2445: zag med lam du dngos su 'jog cing bskur ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:2448: ri mo bzhengs gsol phan nus bskur //
NK063(gu)003:2449: zhes pas lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:2450: dkyil 'khor bstan la shes rab sbyin //
NK063(gu)003:2452: gsang dbang bskur ba'i sor bzhi pa //
NK063(gu)003:2453: zhes pa mkha'i dkyil 'khor la brten pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2459: rtsa ba rnam lnga bco brgyad dang //
NK063(gu)003:2460: zhes pas dad pa can la phan pa'i dbang bcu dang /
NK063(gu)003:2461: brtson 'grus can la nus dbang lnga dang /
NK063(gu)003:2462: brtul zhugs can la zab mo'i dbang gsum mo //
NK063(gu)003:2465: bsgyur ba lnga la zhes pas /
NK063(gu)003:2466: brtsi ba'i grangs lngar gsal te /
NK063(gu)003:2468: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)003:2470: khro bo rdo rje las rim las /
NK063(gu)003:2471: lha dbang phyag mtshan rgyan chas dang //
NK063(gu)003:2472: sgrub rdzas gsang ba rnam gsum mo //
NK063(gu)003:2477: dbu rgyan phyag mtshan gzungs ma bum //
NK063(gu)003:2478: bkra shis rdzas brgyad rat+na bdun //
NK063(gu)003:2479: gdan khri rgyan chas ming 'khor lo //
NK063(gu)003:2482: nyan dang las bzhi 'chad pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:2483: rdo rje rgyal po gdan khri dang //
NK063(gu)003:2484: rat+na bdun dang phyag rgya dang //
NK063(gu)003:2485: ye shes lnga dang sku gsung thugs //
NK063(gu)003:2486: bkra shis rdzas brgyad ming dbang ngo //
NK063(gu)003:2488: sgrub pa'i dbang bcu gsum ni /
NK063(gu)003:2489: shes rab rig dbang khams gsum sgyur //
NK063(gu)003:2490: 'gro don rdzogs byed thong gshol dang //
NK063(gu)003:2491: drug gsum gdan sprugs thod tshar gsum //
NK063(gu)003:2492: srid gsum dag byed mtshon bya dang //
NK063(gu)003:2493: spyod bzhin ma chags 'dod yon lnga //
NK063(gu)003:2494: rnam bzhi'i las rdzogs tir dbyug tho //
NK063(gu)003:2495: don dam dbyer med sbrul chun dang //
NK063(gu)003:2496: gnyis med sbyor rtags lha mo yum //
NK063(gu)003:2497: bdag nyid chen mo longs spyod tshogs //
NK063(gu)003:2498: mnga' bdag chen po sgrub rdzas dang //
NK063(gu)003:2499: grags chen rdo rje ming dbang dang //
NK063(gu)003:2500: sbas pa gsang ba'i dbang dag go //
NK063(gu)003:2502: zab mo'i dbang gnyis ni shes rab ye shes dang /
NK063(gu)003:2505: dbang ma thob bzhin rang byan du spyad pas 'bad
NK063(gu)003:2506: pa'i 'bras bu med cing ngan 'gror ltung ba ste
NK063(gu)003:2508: gsang ba nyams pas ltung 'jigs pa //
NK063(gu)003:2509: so ma btang ba'i rdzas spyod ltar //
NK063(gu)003:2510: 'gyur ba gsang ba'i rgyud kun ltos //
NK063(gu)003:2513: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK063(gu)003:2514: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK063(gu)003:2515: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //
NK063(gu)003:2519: las rtsom 'bras med ltung bas skyon //
NK063(gu)003:2522: gnas skabs su bde ba dang mthar thug bde ba chen po thob pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2523: 'di dang phyi ma phan yon grangs //
NK063(gu)003:2524: rgyud las gsungs pa ji bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:2527: bskur bas skye gnas las nyon mongs //
NK063(gu)003:2528: shes sgrib cha phra rnam dag nas /
NK063(gu)003:2529: yon tan snang phyir ming du brjod //
NK063(gu)003:2531: phyir mi ldog pas yon tan no //
NK063(gu)003:2534: bco lnga pa sngon byung gis ston la /
NK063(gu)003:2537: bcu gsum pas rjes 'jug gi dbang ston no //
NK063(gu)003:2538: lnga pa dam tshig la drug las /
NK063(gu)003:2540: ngan 'gror mi ltung zhing lam dang 'bras bu'i gzhi 'dzin pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2541: rang spyi gdul bya'i bsag sbyang ba'i //
NK063(gu)003:2548: de gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:2551: bsrung bya'i sems sa bon dang bcas pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2553: gsang sgor zhugs pa thams cad kyis //
NK063(gu)003:2554: sgo gsum rang gi bsrung bya las //
NK063(gu)003:2555: rgyal po'i bka' rtags ji lta bar //
NK063(gu)003:2556: mi 'bral sdom pa de ngo bo //
NK063(gu)003:2560: 'dul dang sdom pa dam tshig tshogs //
NK063(gu)003:2561: 'dus par gsungs pa che ba'i mchog /
NK063(gu)003:2563: 'di'i dam tshig tu 'og ma'i bsrung bya rnams 'dus pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:2564: smos pa bla med bsrung thub na //
NK063(gu)003:2565: tshul khrims sdom pa thams cad rdzogs //
NK063(gu)003:2568: bla med mchog go dam tshig tu //
NK063(gu)003:2569: 'dul pa'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK063(gu)003:2570: ji snyed sdom pa mtha' yas pa //
NK063(gu)003:2571: ma lus rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK063(gu)003:2573: tha ma ni khog gzhung las /
NK063(gu)003:2574: rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2575: zhes pas gnyis su med pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2577: bya byed med par nyams pa med //
NK063(gu)003:2580: dam tshig rnams ni rdo rje che //
NK063(gu)003:2581: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK063(gu)003:2584: sa ma ya'i sgras dam tshig ste /
NK063(gu)003:2585: de ni bsrung bya las 'da' bar dka' ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:2587: skyon yon cha yis ched che ba //
NK063(gu)003:2588: de dang de yi nges tshig 'grub //
NK063(gu)003:2590: thub pa'i yon tan gyi dbang du ma ka yo
NK063(gu)003:2591: na'i rkyen gyis bsrung bya la rnam par gnas pas
NK063(gu)003:2592: gnas ngan par mi 'jug pa'i phyir dam zhes bya
NK063(gu)003:2593: la / de ston pa'i lam ni ma nor bden pa'i tshig yin pas na tshig ces bya ste /
NK063(gu)003:2595: gzungs su gyur pas dam zhes bya //
NK063(gu)003:2596: rdo rje ma nor lam ston pa //
NK063(gu)003:2597: de la yang ni tshig ces bya //
NK063(gu)003:2600: ye ma ka na'i rkyen gyis bsrung bya las 'da' bar dka' bas dam zhes bya la /
NK063(gu)003:2601: ji srid 'das na rang gi rgyud 'tshig pa'i phyir dam tshig ces bya ste /
NK063(gu)003:2603: yang na de bzhin bka' bcag na //
NK063(gu)003:2610: mnyam pa cig car ba'i ni /
NK063(gu)003:2612: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK063(gu)003:2613: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK063(gu)003:2614: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2616: dbye ba rim gyis pa'i dam tshig go //
NK063(gu)003:2619: de las phye ba'i rnam grangs so //
NK063(gu)003:2621: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga ste /
NK063(gu)003:2623: bla med mi spang bla ma bkur //
NK063(gu)003:2624: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK063(gu)003:2625: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK063(gu)003:2626: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK063(gu)003:2628: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu ni /
NK063(gu)003:2629: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK063(gu)003:2630: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK063(gu)003:2631: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK063(gu)003:2632: dag pa'i snod bcud mi 'dor ro //
NK063(gu)003:2634: gnyis pa la yang gnyis te /
NK063(gu)003:2638: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las dgu bcu rtsa bdun du gsungs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2640: spong pa rdo rje zhes bya ba'i dam tshig ces pa la sogs pa'i rnam grangs so //
NK063(gu)003:2644: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga gnyis las //
NK063(gu)003:2645: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gsum du dbye //
NK063(gu)003:2646: yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis las //
NK063(gu)003:2647: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye //
NK063(gu)003:2649: mtha' yas par spro ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:2650: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK063(gu)003:2651: 'jigs rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK063(gu)003:2652: srid gsum 'gro ba ji snyed pa //
NK063(gu)003:2655: zhor la dus ni lam thams cad du'o //
NK063(gu)003:2656: zag bcas dngos su bsrung zhing zag med shugs la ldan pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2661: rtsa ba nyams pa'i skyon ni /
NK063(gu)003:2662: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK063(gu)003:2663: sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2664: yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs pa'i //
NK063(gu)003:2667: yan lag nyams pa'i skyon ni /
NK063(gu)003:2668: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK063(gu)003:2669: 'bras bu med cing ngan song ltung //
NK063(gu)003:2671: nyams pa dang 'grogs pa'i skyon ni //
NK063(gu)003:2672: rtsa ba nyams pa'i phyal ba dag /
NK063(gu)003:2673: gso la nye bar mi brtson na //
NK063(gu)003:2674: skad cig yud la smra ma byed //
NK063(gu)003:2675: nyams gyur nyes pa brjod mi lang //
NK063(gu)003:2678: nyams na bskang bas rdzogs pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:2679: nges tshig nges par grub pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:2681: ma nyams pa'i yon tan ni /
NK063(gu)003:2683: bsgrub bya rgyud la smin pa ste //
NK063(gu)003:2684: ma nor gnas pa'i yon tan ni //
NK063(gu)003:2685: rnam grangs rjes 'jug spyir rgyud grags //
NK063(gu)003:2688: gzhan yang rgyal mchog kun bzang gi //
NK063(gu)003:2689: thams cad ma lus phyag rgya yis //
NK063(gu)003:2690: bsgrub med dam pa ma lus 'grub //
NK063(gu)003:2692: de ni bcu dgu pas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:2693: drug pa phrin las la drug las /
NK063(gu)003:2695: rgyud 'byang zhing bdag gzhan gyi don grub pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2697: bdag dang gzhan dang gnyis ka dang //
NK063(gu)003:2698: dam chos phyir na rnam lnga'o //
NK063(gu)003:2701: don bya ba'i yul la byed pa gang zhig tshad
NK063(gu)003:2702: med dang ba'i rgyud las byung zhing thabs kyis zin
NK063(gu)003:2704: phyi rol tshad med nyid las bzhi //
NK063(gu)003:2705: lhag pa gzugs brnyan rnam gnyis dang //
NK063(gu)003:2706: mchod rten sgo dang sbyin sreg ste //
NK063(gu)003:2710: de ni las bzhis rang gzhan gyi don byed pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:2712: zug rngu phyi nang zhi phyir dang //
NK063(gu)003:2713: spel bya gnyis po 'phel phyir dang //
NK063(gu)003:2714: dgug dbang bzhi po bsdu phyir dang //
NK063(gu)003:2715: gdug pa rnam gnyis 'joms phyir dang //
NK063(gu)003:2716: lnga pa don du bstan bzhin phyir //
NK063(gu)003:2717: nges tshig nges par 'grub pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:2719: phrin ni rnam pa bzhi yin te //
NK063(gu)003:2720: las ni so so'i dgos pa skong //
NK063(gu)003:2727: don gyis dmigs su gzung ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:2728: rang bzhin lam dang thugs rje che //
NK063(gu)003:2729: zhes pas spyir gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las /
NK063(gu)003:2730: 'dir lam gyi phrin las la bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)003:2732: don byed pa'i phrin las dang /
NK063(gu)003:2733: don bya thabs kyi rnam grangs dang /
NK063(gu)003:2734: don byed tshul gyi khyad par ro //
NK063(gu)003:2740: gdul bya phyi nang zung bzhi po //
NK063(gu)003:2750: gtso bo'i sems gang gis dang /
NK063(gu)003:2751: gzungs ma gang la brten te dang /
NK063(gu)003:2752: nam gyi tshe bya ba'i dus so //
NK063(gu)003:2755: mchod rten phyag rgya'i sgo dang ni //
NK063(gu)003:2756: hom bro glu dang rdzas kyis bya //
NK063(gu)003:2758: mchod rten gyi sgo nas ni /
NK063(gu)003:2761: bgegs kyi ling ga mnan par bya //
NK063(gu)003:2762: gtum po rngams pa'ang lhan ner 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2763: mi mthun phyogs rnams rdul du rlog /
NK063(gu)003:2765: phyag rgya'i sgo nas bya ba la gnyis las /
NK063(gu)003:2768: yan lag dbang po rtse gcig dang //
NK063(gu)003:2769: rtse lnga rtse dgu bcu gcig tu //
NK063(gu)003:2770: las rnams so sor rab tu sgoms //
NK063(gu)003:2773: rgyas pa'i bcu gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)003:2774: rdo rje lan gsum gsor ba yis //
NK063(gu)003:2775: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK063(gu)003:2778: rdzas kyi sgo nas bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)003:2780: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK063(gu)003:2782: lu gu rgyud kyi bro'i sgo nas ni /
NK063(gu)003:2783: lug gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams nas //
NK063(gu)003:2785: me'i sgo nas phrin las bya ba ni gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:2786: phyi lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dang /
NK063(gu)003:2787: nang khams bzhi'i ni snying gar zhi ba /
NK063(gu)003:2791: gsang ba khams gsum gyi sbyin sreg ni dbang po dang yul dang rnam shes so //
NK063(gu)003:2792: gnyis pa gtso bo'i sems ni don gyi sems gnyis
NK063(gu)003:2793: med rtogs pa las bzhi char la khyab byed du
NK063(gu)003:2794: dgos la / stongs kyi sems ni /
NK063(gu)003:2796: dang bas dga' bas chags pas dang //
NK063(gu)003:2797: khros pas ka li rab tu bya //
NK063(gu)003:2799: gsum pa gzungs ma gang la brten pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:2801: na so gzhon dang rigs 'phel dang //
NK063(gu)003:2802: skye brgyud med dang zla bral dang //
NK063(gu)003:2803: las bzhi'i dus su sbyar ba shis //
NK063(gu)003:2804: las kyi nus mthu cher bstan phyir //
NK063(gu)003:2805: sngon nas btsal ba rab tu gces //
NK063(gu)003:2807: bzhi pa dus nam gyi tshe bya ba ni //
NK063(gu)003:2809: ngo bo rjes su zhi ba gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:2810: phyi la bgegs dgra zhi ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:2811: nang la nyon mongs rtog zhi ba //
NK063(gu)003:2812: rgyas pa gnyis po gos dang 'phel //
NK063(gu)003:2813: na shi lo tog sre'u sogs //
NK063(gu)003:2814: tshe dang rigs brgyad longs spyod dang //
NK063(gu)003:2816: dbang ni dgug dang bsdu ba gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:2817: phyi rol d+ha ri'i rnam pa dgug /
NK063(gu)003:2818: mi mthun rnam gnyis dbang po bsgyur //
NK063(gu)003:2819: rang sems 'bras lnga bsdu bar bya //
NK063(gu)003:2820: mngon spyod bskrad dang mnan pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:2822: rmongs dang brtan po rgyud gzhan la'o //
NK063(gu)003:2823: rang gi phyi nang dgra bgegs 'joms //
NK063(gu)003:2824: zhes pas de dag gi dus su'o //
NK063(gu)003:2827: khyad par zag bcas bar chad med //
NK063(gu)003:2828: mthar phyin lam gyi phye ba'am //
NK063(gu)003:2829: shes rab dbang po rnam gsum gyis //
NK063(gu)003:2830: nus mthu byin brlabs yul ngo bo //
NK063(gu)003:2831: thabs dang gzhi la khyad par ba //
NK063(gu)003:2832: gan tsa lta bu ji lta ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:2835: skabs ni dbang dang sgrub pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:2836: mchod bshags tshe dang dus bab tshe //
NK063(gu)003:2840: mi skong mi rdzogs mi 'byang dang //
NK063(gu)003:2841: don gnyis mi 'grub de yi skyon //
NK063(gu)003:2845: de las ldog pa'i tshul bstan pa //
NK063(gu)003:2846: yon tan nyid du shes par bya //
NK063(gu)003:2849: gtum po rngams pa'ang lhan ner 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2851: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK063(gu)003:2853: sangs rgyas gsung yang dbang du 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2855: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK063(gu)003:2858: nyi shu pa nas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:2859: bdun pa sgrub pa la drug las //
NK063(gu)003:2861: sgrub pa'i thabs yal bar ma dor bas bsgrub bya gnyis mngon du gyur pa nii /
NK063(gu)003:2863: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NK063(gu)003:2864: bdag gzhan thob nas don bzhi'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:2867: gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshang nas thabs bsnyen
NK063(gu)003:2868: sgrub bzhis bsgrub bya don du gnyer bzhin pa zhig
NK063(gu)003:2869: ste / gang gis gang thob 'dod pa ste //
NK063(gu)003:2870: yan lag bcu ldan gnyer bsngo ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:2873: yan lag ma nyams yo byad ldan //
NK063(gu)003:2874: cho ga rdzogs par shes pa yis //
NK063(gu)003:2876: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK063(gu)003:2881: de thabs kyis nyams su blangs pas grub pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:2882: don du gnyer phyir sgrub mtshan nges //
NK063(gu)003:2891: gang zhig lha chen po la sogs 'jig rten 'di'i
NK063(gu)003:2892: 'dod bya gtso bor ston pa thun mong gi dang
NK063(gu)003:2893: / gang zhig rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa
NK063(gu)003:2894: mthar thug gi bsgrub bya gtso bor ston pa mchog
NK063(gu)003:2895: / dang / gang zhig de dag gi bsgrub pa'i tshul gtso bor ston pa tshogs sgrub pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2899: longs spyod 'byung zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK063(gu)003:2901: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing //
NK063(gu)003:2903: chu rgyun 'bab pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)003:2905: thams cad stong shing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2906: dgug dang gtang dang bcing dang dgrol //
NK063(gu)003:2907: gso dang gsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK063(gu)003:2911: ro langs tshe pra sgrub pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:2912: lha chen po dang rgyal po bzhi //
NK063(gu)003:2913: gdug pa klu 'dul rgyal blon gyi //
NK063(gu)003:2914: chung ma dbang du bya ba gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:2915: ro langs dam tshig rkang mgyogs bskrad //
NK063(gu)003:2916: mi snang gzugs sgrub lha klu mo //
NK063(gu)003:2917: rgyal blon dpon dang zhang blon sgrub //
NK063(gu)003:2923: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK063(gu)003:2924: phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon rdzogs pa //
NK063(gu)003:2928: yi ge sgyu 'phrul tshogs sgrub dang //
NK063(gu)003:2929: rdo rje sems dpa' sman sgrub dang //
NK063(gu)003:2930: rigs lnga sgrub dang yum lnga sems //
NK063(gu)003:2931: byin rlabs sgrub pa rnam gnyis so //
NK063(gu)003:2936: sngags dang phyag rgya brtan pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:2937: mi lcogs med pa gang yod dang //
NK063(gu)003:2938: cha rkyen tshang bas dbang sgyur sngon //
NK063(gu)003:2942: skabs kyis gtso dang grogs pos bsdus //
NK063(gu)003:2943: zhes pas rgyud don gzhan dgu char yin te /
NK063(gu)003:2944: de las drug sngon du bstan la /
NK063(gu)003:2948: cha rkyen tshang bas dbang bas dbang sgyur sngon //
NK063(gu)003:2949: zhes pas tshe dbang gi sngon du gcig spros mthar phyin nas sgrub pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:2950: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK063(gu)003:2951: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:2954: yal bas mi 'byang mi thob bcu //
NK063(gu)003:2955: bye brag rgyas pa khong du chud //
NK063(gu)003:2960: lnga lnga 'thob la don gnyer rdzogs //
NK063(gu)003:2963: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK063(gu)003:2965: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK063(gu)003:2972: bcu gsum pa rnams kyis ston no //
NK063(gu)003:2973: brgyad pa ting nge 'dzin la drug las /
NK063(gu)003:2975: rtogs pa'i ngang la gnas pas 'khor ba la dbang sgyur ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:2977: rtog pa dbang sgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK063(gu)003:2980: sgom pa'i thabs kyi bsgom bya las mi g.yo bar gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:2982: mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas su //
NK063(gu)003:2985: sa ma ti'i sgras ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK063(gu)003:2986: de ni rtse gcig par gnas pas bsgom bya mi gtong ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:2995: mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas su //
NK063(gu)003:2996: zhes pas mnyam bzhag gi dus so //
NK063(gu)003:3000: rgya mtsho'i 'jing gi pha bong ltar //
NK063(gu)003:3001: bskal par lam la btsal byas kyang //
NK063(gu)003:3002: don med snying po bskams pa yin //
NK063(gu)003:3007: bsgrub pa'i gtsor ni ting 'dzin pas //
NK063(gu)003:3011: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK063(gu)003:3012: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:3014: de ni lnga pa dang bcu gsum pa la sogs pas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:3015: dgu pa mchod pa la drug las /
NK063(gu)003:3017: rgyud 'byang zhing dam skong ba dang lha mnyes shing don bzhi rdzogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3019: bdag gzhan don rdzogs mnyes skongs pa //
NK063(gu)003:3022: mchod bya'i yul gang zhig mnyes par byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3024: bya byed bya ba byed 'dus pas //
NK063(gu)003:3025: dgyes tshim 'gyur ba'i dngos po nyid //
NK063(gu)003:3028: p+au dza'i sgras mchod pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3029: de yang pur pa dza'i rkyen gyis sngon du sngon du skyed par byed pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3030: pur na pur na tri yang dza ha'i rkyen gyis yang dang yang du dgyes pa bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3031: pu dza tha gor wa tha na'i rkyen gyis bkur ba'i phyir mchod pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3036: thun mong phyi'i dang khyad par nang gi dang /
NK063(gu)003:3037: gsang ba bla med rmad du byung ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:3039: phyi nang gsang ba'i rdzas dgongs mchod //
NK063(gu)003:3040: srog dang ldan pa rten gsum tshul //
NK063(gu)003:3042: zhar la 'bul thabs ni lta ba dang ting nge
NK063(gu)003:3043: 'dzin gyi khyad par gyis rim gyis dang cig car
NK063(gu)003:3044: te / rim gyis yang na cir car du //
NK063(gu)003:3051: las sbyong sgrub dbang mchod tshe na //
NK063(gu)003:3055: de las ldog dang mi skong g.yel //
NK063(gu)003:3056: nyams chad mthu byin bral bar 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:3060: dus kyi rjes zhugs yon tan dag /
NK063(gu)003:3061: spyi dang khyad par skabs kyis ni //
NK063(gu)003:3063: bdag gzhan don gyis gnyis su 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:3065: de ni dgu pa dang bco brgyad pas so //
NK063(gu)003:3066: tha ma sngags dang phyag rgya la drug las //
NK063(gu)003:3068: bar chad sel zhing nus pa bskyed pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3070: sbyang zhing nye bar bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3071: thob bya lnga po rdzogs bya'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3073: ngo bo la sngags kyi ni /
NK063(gu)003:3074: +aa li k+aa li'i ste yi ge'i go rim sbyar bas nus pa mthu can du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:3076: yi ge 'dus pas grub pa bzhi //
NK063(gu)003:3077: mthu can red pa gang yin pa //
NK063(gu)003:3080: bskyed rim gyi yan lag rdzogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3082: bzhi rdzogs nyid las mi 'da' ba //
NK063(gu)003:3083: gang la snang ba de ngo bo //
NK063(gu)003:3086: man+t+ra mu tra'i sgras sngags dang phyag rgya ste /
NK063(gu)003:3087: ye shes snying po'i le'u bdun pa las /
NK063(gu)003:3088: a ni yid ces bya ba ste //
NK063(gu)003:3089: tra ni skyob pa nyid du bshad //
NK063(gu)003:3091: yid skyob cing byin rlabs 'byung ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:3092: mi 'da' ba'am 'ching zhing sdom pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:3101: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK063(gu)003:3106: skyon brgyad spangs pa'i brtson pas sbyar //
NK063(gu)003:3109: sgra cher ma yin chung bar min //
NK063(gu)003:3110: mgyogs par ma yin bul bar min //
NK063(gu)003:3111: drag par ma yin zhan par min //
NK063(gu)003:3112: yig 'bru yan lag nyams par min //
NK063(gu)003:3113: yengs dang phyal sogs bar chad pa //
NK063(gu)003:3114: rgyu ba'i bsam pa spangs pa dang //
NK063(gu)003:3116: bzhi pa bskul ba phrin las kyi sngags so //
NK063(gu)003:3117: gnyis pa la yang bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)003:3118: sku phyag rgya chen po mi bskyod pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3119: g.yas pa'i gung mo thugs kar bkan thabs su bca' ba bca' ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK063(gu)003:3120: h+aum mthing nag yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje
NK063(gu)003:3121: 'od 'bar ba bsam pa ni bsam pa dam rgya'o
NK063(gu)003:3122: // rdo rje'i rtser h+aum sgra dang bcas pa bsam pa ni bsam pa chos kyi'o //
NK063(gu)003:3123: g.yon pa dril bu gsil zhing g.yon du yum bsam pa ni bsam pa las kyi'o //
NK063(gu)003:3124: zhabs g.yon pa pad+ma'i rigs su brlabs te /
NK063(gu)003:3125: yum dang 'khyil thabs su bca' ba bca' ba las kyi'o //
NK063(gu)003:3126: ngag tu h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika brjod pa brjod pa chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK063(gu)003:3130: mchod phrin gtso bor bsgrub pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3132: gsung gi dam tshig nyams shing 'bras bu med par 'gyur ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:3134: ral gri'i so la bzung nyes ltar //
NK063(gu)003:3135: nan tan med pa'i gsang sngags pa //
NK063(gu)003:3140: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK063(gu)003:3141: dngos grub ya mtshan cher 'gyur bas //
NK063(gu)003:3142: yid la bsam pa thams cad 'grub //
NK063(gu)003:3146: bcu drug pa rnams nas so //
NK063(gu)003:3147: rgyud kyi dgos 'brel la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)003:3149: phas kyi rgol ba tshar gcad pa dang des rtogs ldan bstan pa la 'jug pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3151: rgyud la ldan phyir rgol ba zlog /
NK063(gu)003:3153: rgol ba po dag tshar gcad phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3157: rjod dang 'brel pa dgos yang dgos //
NK063(gu)003:3158: zhes pas yan lag bzhi pa nyid do //
NK063(gu)003:3160: de dag rgyud la tshang ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:3164: dang po la yan lag bzhi las /
NK063(gu)003:3167: brjod pa brjod bya rjod byed de //
NK063(gu)003:3170: brda btags pa la brten nas don go byar gnas pa ste rang bzhin gyi rgyud de yin te /
NK063(gu)003:3172: mtshon bya rang bzhin gzhi yi rgyud //
NK063(gu)003:3175: sgra dang tshig la brten nas don go byed du
NK063(gu)003:3176: gyur pa ste mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud rnams te
NK063(gu)003:3177: / mtshon byed sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste //
NK063(gu)003:3180: don du gnyer bar bya ba ste //
NK063(gu)003:3182: don du gnyer phyir dgos pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3184: de 'dir gang brjod bya rtogs pa zhig yin te /
NK063(gu)003:3185: mdzub mos ri bong can bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:3188: don du gnyer bya mthar thug pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3190: dgos pa'i dgos pa 'bras bu nyid //
NK063(gu)003:3192: de 'dir mthar thug gi 'bras bu mthar phyin pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3194: dgos pa 'grub phyir yang dgos so //
NK063(gu)003:3197: sprin med na mi 'byung ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:3201: de las phye bas bdag gcig pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)003:3202: de las 'byung ba'i 'brel ba gnyis so //
NK063(gu)003:3203: 'dir brjod bya'i don rjod byed kyis brjod pa ni thabs yin la /
NK063(gu)003:3204: don rtogs pa ni thabs las byung ba'i phyir de gnyis de dang 'brel zhing /
NK063(gu)003:3205: yang don rtogs pa ni rgyu yin la sangs rgyas
NK063(gu)003:3206: pa ni 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir de gnyis rgyu
NK063(gu)003:3209: mtshon bya mtshon byed rgyu 'bras tshul //
NK063(gu)003:3211: don gnyis pa yang gong ltar yan lag bzhi las /
NK063(gu)003:3212: dang po la gnyis kyi brjod bya ni /
NK063(gu)003:3214: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ni //
NK063(gu)003:3215: zhes mthun zer kyang don tha dad de /
NK063(gu)003:3216: 'dir gsang ba'i yul dang dbang po 'phrad pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3218: thig le chen po thabs dang bcas pa'o zhes pa
NK063(gu)003:3219: 'khor lo sgyur ba drug la sogs byed pa sdom
NK063(gu)003:3221: dga' ba bcu drug gis thig le bzhi bcu rtsa
NK063(gu)003:3222: gnyis kyi bde ba nyams su myong ba ni dga'
NK063(gu)003:3223: ba mchog dga' dga' bral lhan cig skyes pa'i dga'
NK063(gu)003:3224: ba ste rtsa ba bzhi las bye brag bzhi bzhir
NK063(gu)003:3227: de dag rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi ye shes su mngon du byas pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3229: gong ltar ram yang na yang dgos dgos pa las byung zhing de brjod bya las byung ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3230: de ni rgyud dbu zhabs thams cad nas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:3231: bstan pa gdams shing gtad pa la gsum las dgos pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:3232: bstan pa yal bar mi 'dor bas gces spras su 'dzin pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3233: nges tshig ni bka' stsal ba'i rgyud de zungs shig par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:3234: ngo bo dang rnam grangs thun mong pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)003:3235: spyir rgyud dbu zhabs kyi brjod bya snang ba bzhir 'dus la /
NK063(gu)003:3236: snang ba bzhi yang rang bzhin gyi snang ba bzhii'i
NK063(gu)003:3237: rgyud du 'dus te ye nas sangs rgyas pa las
NK063(gu)003:3238: mi 'gyur bas de'i don la rtogs shig sgrubs shig
NK063(gu)003:3239: 'bod cig par gdams pa yin te /
NK063(gu)003:3241: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK063(gu)003:3242: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK063(gu)003:3244: rgyud gtad pa dngos ni thugs thigs las /
NK063(gu)003:3245: ston pa gang gis gang nyid la //
NK063(gu)003:3246: gtad pa gang de ci yi phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3254: 'chad pa'i skyes bus gtad pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3256: ston pa rang byung rdo rje 'dzin //
NK063(gu)003:3257: rgyal tshab rgyud ni skyes bu gnyis //
NK063(gu)003:3262: sdud pa po dang bud med dang //
NK063(gu)003:3263: rnal 'byor mig ldan la sogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3266: rgyal tshab rgyud kyi ston par dbyung ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:3267: brtan cing byin che ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:3268: dar zhing rgyas pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)003:3270: rtogs dang bsrung dang gdams pa yis //
NK063(gu)003:3272: mi nub bstan pa yun ring phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3276: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK063(gu)003:3277: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //
NK063(gu)003:3278: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yi //
NK063(gu)003:3279: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK063(gu)003:3280: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK063(gu)003:3281: zhes pas sdud pa po la dang /
NK063(gu)003:3282: gang zag chos min can la dang /
NK063(gu)003:3283: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro la gtad tshul lo //
NK063(gu)003:3284: de dag gi phyir tha snyad tsam du gtad ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)003:3285: de ni le'u tha mas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:3286: dbang po tha ma la 'bru re gnyer res bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:3288: shes rab tha ma'i don bstan pa //
NK063(gu)003:3289: bshad tshul snod dang sbyar ba ste //
NK063(gu)003:3290: zhes pas spyir 'di blo rab kyi spyod yul yin la /
NK063(gu)003:3291: de'i tha ma'i don du mtshon byed kyi rgyud 'di
NK063(gu)003:3292: dag gi bshad thabs kyi yan lag ni bcu ste
NK063(gu)003:3294: lta nyid de bzhin sgo 'byed dang //
NK063(gu)003:3295: spyi sdud pa dang sbyor bar 'brel //
NK063(gu)003:3296: rang rkyen ldem dgongs gal po'i tshig /
NK063(gu)003:3297: ma bcos de bzhin mtshon pa'i dpe //
NK063(gu)003:3298: cho rol snel gzhi rnam pa kun //
NK063(gu)003:3299: me long bcu dang mthun par sbyar //
NK063(gu)003:3300: zhes pas rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig khyung nam mkha' la lding ba ltar bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:3302: ka la pang+ki'i chos bzhi pos //
NK063(gu)003:3305: mig gong du mi blta ba dang gcig /
NK063(gu)003:3306: gshog pa g.yob pa'i rtsol ba med pa dang gnyis /
NK063(gu)003:3307: ngam grog dang g.yang sa la nyam mi nga ba dang gsum /
NK063(gu)003:3308: kha 'og tu chud pa'i chos gsal ba bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)003:3310: 'di'i gong na rtogs bya gzhan med pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3311: gnyis pa ni ltung gnas la nyam mi nga ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3312: gsum pa ni lam bgrod pa'i rtsol ba dang bral ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3313: bzhi pa ni 'og ma'i lta ba rnams kha 'og tu chud pa'i chos gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3314: rnam par 'byed pa'i tshig stag gis mchongs pa ltar ni /
NK063(gu)003:3316: b+y+aa kri mchongs pa de bzhin pas //
NK063(gu)003:3317: rgyud kyi tshig don dum bur gcod //
NK063(gu)003:3319: bgrod par bya ba'i sa tshigs gcig yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3320: sa tshoms su bcad nas mchongs pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3321: dang po ni dkyus dbu zhabs kyi don no //
NK063(gu)003:3322: gnyis pa ni gzhung rnams tshoms su gcod pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3323: spyi don sdud pa'i tshig seng ge'i mchongs pa ltar ni /
NK063(gu)003:3325: seng chen mchongs pa'i chos gcig ltar //
NK063(gu)003:3326: rnam grangs tshig lam don gcig sdud //
NK063(gu)003:3328: bgrod par bya ba'i sa tshigs gcig yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3329: sa khams du ma kha 'og tu chud pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3330: dang po ni sa tshigs dang 'dra bar dkyus dbu zhabs kyi don no //
NK063(gu)003:3331: gnyis pa dbye ba mang po rnams gcig tu sdud pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3332: 'brel pa sbyor ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros ltar ni /
NK063(gu)003:3334: ngang mo'i 'gros chos rnam gnyis ltar //
NK063(gu)003:3335: gzhan don dbu zhabs le'u mtshams sbyor //
NK063(gu)003:3337: sngar rjes phyi rjes kyis non par 'gro ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:3339: dang po sngar bshad zin dang phyis 'chad pa rnams rjes kyis non pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3340: gnyis pa tshig don mngon rtogs sa lam la sogs 'brel pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3341: rang rkyen gnyer gyis rus sbal gyis nur 'gros ltar ni /
NK063(gu)003:3343: rus sbal 'gros kyi chos gsum po //
NK063(gu)003:3344: 'bru stong mi gzhag gzer gnyis gdab //
NK063(gu)003:3346: bgrod par bya ba'i sa tshigs dang /
NK063(gu)003:3347: 'gror mi mngon par rjes kyis 'gengs pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3348: 'gror mi mngon yang dus lan cig phyin pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3349: dang po ni dkyus dbu zhabs kyi don no //
NK063(gu)003:3350: gnyis pa tshig re nas bshad pas rdzogs par mi mngon /
NK063(gu)003:3351: gsum pa mi mngon yang gzhung rdzogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3352: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig rna phrug brag la 'dzeg pa ltar ni /
NK063(gu)003:3354: rna phug 'dzeg pa'i chos nyid ltar //
NK063(gu)003:3355: ldem dgongs gsang ba brgyad kyis sbyar //
NK063(gu)003:3357: rna phrug gis brag nyi ma 'char tshad la thar ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:3358: de ri dwags gzhan la mi 'tshams yang de nyid la 'tshams pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3359: dang po ni thabs dang ldan pas 'ching ba gcod pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3360: gnyis pa de 'og ma'i yul min yang 'di'i 'o //
NK063(gu)003:3361: gtar ka gegs sel gyi tshig bya glag gzan la 'jums pa ltar ni /
NK063(gu)003:3363: glag gi gzan gyi chos gnyis ltar //
NK063(gu)003:3364: don gyi dmigs gzung gegs bsal lo //
NK063(gu)003:3367: khong na gnas pa'i bcud de zos pas glag gi nyams rtsal rgyas pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3368: dang po bus rtog pa'i yul lo //
NK063(gu)003:3369: gnyis pa slob dpon gyi thugs la gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3370: gsum pa dris shing lan gyis tshim pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3371: mtshon pa dpe'i tshig me long lta bu ni /
NK063(gu)003:3373: me long chos ltar mtshon pa'i dpe //
NK063(gu)003:3374: kun la des mtshon thog tu dbab //
NK063(gu)003:3376: bzhin lkog tu gyur pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3378: dang po gzhung don mi gsal ba rnams so //
NK063(gu)003:3379: gnyis pa de dpes rnam pa gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3380: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig dus kyi 'brug sgra ltar ni /
NK063(gu)003:3382: dus kyi 'brug ltar chos gsum po //
NK063(gu)003:3383: bka' yi tshad gzung skabs sbyar nas //
NK063(gu)003:3387: des skye 'khrungs su yid ches pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3388: dang po drang ba'i yul min par mi drang /
NK063(gu)003:3389: gnyis pa skabs dang mthun par drang /
NK063(gu)003:3390: gsum pa des rang gzhung khegs par yid ches te /
NK063(gu)003:3392: lung ni yid ches gnas yin te /
NK063(gu)003:3393: nyes pa spangs pa rdzun gyi tshig /
NK063(gu)003:3394: smra bar mi 'gyur rgyu med phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3395: nyes zad lung du shes par bya //
NK063(gu)003:3397: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig seng phrug rtsal sbyong ba ltar bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:3398: mi 'jigs phrug gu rtsal sbyong ltar //
NK063(gu)003:3399: 'bru tshig don gyi go rim sdeb //
NK063(gu)003:3402: ma rjes drang por srong ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3403: dang po gong 'og 'khrugs kyis bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3404: gnyis pa don go rim ma nor ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3405: de dag la yang dkyus dbu zhabs thams cad du
NK063(gu)003:3406: khyab byed du 'jug pa gsum la rnam par 'byed
NK063(gu)003:3409: khyad par du 'jug pa gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:3413: 'jug tu yang rung ba bzhin no //
NK063(gu)003:3419: tshig don mos par bshad pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3420: rnam par phye bas ma 'dres gsal //
NK063(gu)003:3422: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba 'bras bu'i rgyud ni /
NK063(gu)003:3423: chos kyi dbyings mngon du gyur pas dag pa sku
NK063(gu)003:3424: dang ye shes su snang ba ni bshad pa'i gzhi
NK063(gu)003:3425: yin te / sku mchog rdo rje 'od snang ba //
NK063(gu)003:3426: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3428: de la bshad na lnga las /
NK063(gu)003:3430: skyon thams cad las grol zhing yon tan ma lus pa lhun gyis rdzogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3431: 'bras bu yon tan lhun grub pas //
NK063(gu)003:3432: yid bzhin nor ltar snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)003:3435: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo rnams so //
NK063(gu)003:3436: 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsung thugs //
NK063(gu)003:3437: yon tan phrin las la sogs pa //
NK063(gu)003:3440: de dag bdag don du grub pa dbyer med rdo rje dang /
NK063(gu)003:3441: des gzhan don mdzad pa'i tshul lo //
NK063(gu)003:3443: ma 'dres rnam grangs su snang ba dang /
NK063(gu)003:3444: dbyer med lhun grub kyi ngo bo dang /
NK063(gu)003:3445: mtshan nyid mtha' bral du bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3451: sku yi phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK063(gu)003:3452: zhes pa che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa'i rten byed pas sku dang /
NK063(gu)003:3453: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK063(gu)003:3454: zhes pas gdul bya la brda sprod pa ste gsung dang /
NK063(gu)003:3455: thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs yin te //
NK063(gu)003:3456: de yis mi mkhyen gang yang med //
NK063(gu)003:3458: yon tan ni mnga' thang rdzogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3459: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3461: phrin las ni gdul bya'i bya ba byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3462: gdul bya thams cad chud ma zos //
NK063(gu)003:3466: de yang skabs kyi lnga lnga ste //
NK063(gu)003:3467: zhes pas re rer yang lnga lnga'o //
NK063(gu)003:3469: rig pa spros bral gyi dbyings mngon du gyur pa chos kyi sku ste /
NK063(gu)003:3471: de bzhin dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK063(gu)003:3473: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK063(gu)003:3475: sna tshogs zag med kyi bde bar longs spyod pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ste /
NK063(gu)003:3476: yang dag thar pa'i gzugs sku dang //
NK063(gu)003:3478: de mi shes kyi gter du 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:3480: de nyid 'gro ba ji ltar mos pa ltar sku sna tshogs su snang ba sprul pa'i sku ste /
NK063(gu)003:3483: mthun byas sku ni sna tshogs ston //
NK063(gu)003:3485: dbyer med kyi don rig pa'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pa rdo rje'i sku ste /
NK063(gu)003:3487: ston nyid sgyu ma mig yor tshul //
NK063(gu)003:3488: tshul nyid dbyings las g.yos pa med //
NK063(gu)003:3490: de dag rig pa'i ye shes la lhun gyis rdzogs pa mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ste /
NK063(gu)003:3492: ma g.yos bzhin du sna tshogs pa'i //
NK063(gu)003:3493: de tshe mi mthun sna tshogs la //
NK063(gu)003:3494: so so 'dra bar snang ba yin //
NK063(gu)003:3497: brjod med don gyi gsung ni /
NK063(gu)003:3499: sgra dang ming tshig kun las 'das //
NK063(gu)003:3500: sna tshogs sgra rnams gsal bar 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:3504: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra zhing //
NK063(gu)003:3505: sku yis chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK063(gu)003:3507: barjooda pa tshig gi gsung ni /
NK063(gu)003:3509: brjod med de nyid sna tshogs sgra //
NK063(gu)003:3510: kun la grags shing so sor 'jal //
NK063(gu)003:3514: sgra nyid ma chags ngang du gsungs //
NK063(gu)003:3515: gsungs pa nyid na brjod du med //
NK063(gu)003:3517: rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung ni //
NK063(gu)003:3519: grol thar lam dang 'khor ba'i sgra //
NK063(gu)003:3520: ji skad brjod kyang gsung mchog ste //
NK063(gu)003:3523: skye med kyi dbyings mngon du gyur pa rnam pa cir yang mi rtog pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3525: stong nyid ye shes dngos po med //
NK063(gu)003:3527: tha dad du 'dzin pa dag pa mnyam pa chen po ste /
NK063(gu)003:3529: mnyam nyid ye shes bzang ngan med //
NK063(gu)003:3531: thugs rjes 'gro ba rnams yang dag pa'i sa la sgrol ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:3533: bya ba'i ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK063(gu)003:3535: chos spyi dang rang mtshan cir yang sa le mkhyen pa'i thugs ni /
NK063(gu)003:3537: kun rtog ye shes ma 'dres gsal //
NK063(gu)003:3539: rgyas pa'i don gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)003:3540: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK063(gu)003:3541: rtsa ba lnga zhes brjod med kyang //
NK063(gu)003:3542: brjod pa'i mtshan nyid yongs med de //
NK063(gu)003:3543: mtshan nyid med par sna tshogs snang //
NK063(gu)003:3544: de nyid thams cad mkhyen pa nyid //
NK063(gu)003:3547: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams ni //
NK063(gu)003:3548: zhing khams rnam dag bsam yas dang //
NK063(gu)003:3550: rgya dang ya ba'i gzhal byas ni //
NK063(gu)003:3552: gsal zhing dag pa'i 'od zer ni //
NK063(gu)003:3553: mthing kha dkar po ser le brgan //
NK063(gu)003:3557: khyad par 'phags pa'i gdan khri ni /
NK063(gu)003:3558: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang zhes pa la sogs dang /
NK063(gu)003:3559: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i zhes so //
NK063(gu)003:3560: dgyes rgur rol pa'i longs spyod ni /
NK063(gu)003:3561: gzugs sna tshogs dang la sogs so //
NK063(gu)003:3563: rtog pa dang zug rngu zhi bas dang /
NK063(gu)003:3564: ye shes dang tshe bsod rgyas pas dang /
NK063(gu)003:3565: rnam rtog gdul bya dbang gis dang //
NK063(gu)003:3566: ma rig pa dang gnod stug drag pos dang //
NK063(gu)003:3567: lhun gyis grub pas don mdzad pa'o //
NK063(gu)003:3568: de dag thams cad don gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)003:3569: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK063(gu)003:3570: bya byed med las rnam bzhir mdzad //
NK063(gu)003:3571: mdzad dang mdzad par bya ba med //
NK063(gu)003:3574: de ltar sku ni re bdun pa las /
NK063(gu)003:3575: bde gshegs sku lnga mdo ru bsdus //
NK063(gu)003:3576: bcom ldan 'das dang byang chub sku //
NK063(gu)003:3577: bla med gzugs dang rdo rje'i sku //
NK063(gu)003:3578: de la sogs pa sku bsam yas //
NK063(gu)003:3581: gsung brjod bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK063(gu)003:3583: lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK063(gu)003:3586: theg pa bsam yas ston pa yang //
NK063(gu)003:3587: de bzhin nyid kyi ma brjod kyang //
NK063(gu)003:3588: sems can blo yi rim pa bzhin //
NK063(gu)003:3589: so sor 'tshams par kun la gsal //
NK063(gu)003:3593: ye shes spyan gyis spras pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3594: zhing dang yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK063(gu)003:3596: phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni /
NK063(gu)003:3598: 'gro ba'i phrin las bsam mi khyab //
NK063(gu)003:3601: lhun grub yon tan rang snang ba //
NK063(gu)003:3603: de dag kyang chos nyid mngon byas kyi ldog pa tha dad pa tsam yin gyi /
NK063(gu)003:3604: ye shes chos kyi dbyings las mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)003:3605: dper na bum pa gcig gi rdzas dang ldog pa lta bu ste /
NK063(gu)003:3606: gnyis med sems su mngon byas pas //
NK063(gu)003:3607: bden gnyis dbyer med rdo rje'i sku //
NK063(gu)003:3608: chu yi zla ba lta bu ba //
NK063(gu)003:3609: rang bzhin dang ba tha mi dad //
NK063(gu)003:3613: mtshan nyid gcig dang du ma med //
NK063(gu)003:3615: de'ang mtha' gang du'ang ma grub pa'i phyir bzhi char
NK063(gu)003:3616: yin pa'i thams cad du lhun gyis grub pa ste
NK063(gu)003:3618: mtshan nyid bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3619: ma lus gcig min tha dad min //
NK063(gu)003:3621: mtshan nyid gcig dang du ma med //
NK063(gu)003:3624: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK063(gu)003:3625: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK063(gu)003:3626: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK063(gu)003:3627: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK063(gu)003:3629: dus gsum rim par rdzogs sangs pa'i //
NK063(gu)003:3630: log rtog tha dad snang ba yang //
NK063(gu)003:3631: ye nas mtha' las grol ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)003:3632: gcig dang mi gcig brjod bsam 'das //
NK063(gu)003:3634: chos gnyis pa la yang don gsum las /
NK063(gu)003:3635: gdul bya gzigs par mdzad pa la /
NK063(gu)003:3637: gzigs lugs rgyas par bstan pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3639: nyid las mi gzhan don nyid kyis //
NK063(gu)003:3640: me long lta bur gzigs par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)003:3642: thugs rje shar bar mdzad pa la /
NK063(gu)003:3643: thugs rje'i rgyu rkyen bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3644: skye tshul rgyas par bshad pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3646: thugs rje chen pos gdul bya la //
NK063(gu)003:3647: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs gsol dang //
NK063(gu)003:3650: shar nas 'gro don mdzad pa la don mdzad pa'i bzhed gzhung tha dad bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3651: mdzad tshul rgyas par bshad pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3653: phrin las rnam bzhi'i mdzad spyod kyis //
NK063(gu)003:3654: bya ba med bzhin don rnams rdzogs //
NK063(gu)003:3656: sgra bshad pa'am ta th+aa ga ta'i sgras de bzhin gshegs pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3657: de zhes pa chos nyid do //
NK063(gu)003:3658: bzhin zhes pa ma bslad pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3660: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa yang //
NK063(gu)003:3662: gshegs pa ni de mngon du byas pas 'bras bu mthar phyin pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3663: sna tshogs zhen las grol bar bshad //
NK063(gu)003:3665: snang ba ni dag pa ye shes su snang ba ste /
NK063(gu)003:3666: sku mchog rdo rje 'od snang ba //
NK063(gu)003:3668: 'bras bu ni lam bgrod pa don yod pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3670: grub pa'i mthar phyin 'bras bur brjod //
NK063(gu)003:3672: rgyud ces pa 'bras bu'i dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel ba dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)003:3674: theg pa thun mong gi 'bras bu smin 'bras dang /
NK063(gu)003:3676: dang po ni rten sku gsum ste /
NK063(gu)003:3678: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK063(gu)003:3679: longs spyod zad med rin chen gter //
NK063(gu)003:3680: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK063(gu)003:3682: brten pa ye shes bzhi ni /
NK063(gu)003:3684: me long ye shes mi g.yo ste //
NK063(gu)003:3685: ye shes gsum ni de la brten //
NK063(gu)003:3688: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las /
NK063(gu)003:3689: nam mkhas ji ltar khyab gyur pa //
NK063(gu)003:3690: mdzad pas kyang ni de snyed khyab //
NK063(gu)003:3694: lhun grub dang bcas pas so //
NK063(gu)003:3699: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni gong du bstan te /
NK063(gu)003:3700: tshe la dbang dang phyag rgya che //
NK063(gu)003:3701: lhun grub ting 'dzin la sogs pa //
NK063(gu)003:3702: lam dang 'bras bu thun mong brjod //
NK063(gu)003:3704: mthar thug gi 'bras bu yang de'i ngo bo'i skabs su zab cing rgya che bar bshad zin to //
NK063(gu)003:3705: zhor la de dag gi don nye bar sbyar ba'i
NK063(gu)003:3706: bshad pa ni 'bras bu de dag gi thob tshul
NK063(gu)003:3708: lam thun mong gi theg pa pa'i lugs kyi sangs
NK063(gu)003:3709: rgyas ni spangs rtogs mthar thug pa zhes bya bar
NK063(gu)003:3710: 'dod de / 'phags pa'i lam du sa bcus spang
NK063(gu)003:3711: bya sgrib pa rnams spangs nas gong gi thob bya
NK063(gu)003:3712: rang gi 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3713: de nas sa bcu rim gyi 'byang //
NK063(gu)003:3714: bla med byang chub yang dag 'thob //
NK063(gu)003:3716: 'dir ni spangs thob dang bral te /
NK063(gu)003:3718: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid du gcig pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)003:3720: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK063(gu)003:3721: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK063(gu)003:3722: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK063(gu)003:3723: de lta bu yi ngang du byung //
NK063(gu)003:3726: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang //
NK063(gu)003:3727: phrin las rmad byung kun grags pa //
NK063(gu)003:3728: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK063(gu)003:3729: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK063(gu)003:3731: ye nas yin pa'i don nyid mngon du byas pas 'bras bu mthar phyin pa ste /
NK063(gu)003:3732: mthar thug bskyed du bya ba med //
NK063(gu)003:3734: lam dang 'bras bur bcas pa yang //
NK063(gu)003:3736: sems can dus nas lhun rdzogs pas //
NK063(gu)003:3751: tha ma rnams nas ston no //
NK063(gu)003:3752: rgyud kyi don spyi'i rnam par bzhag pa rdo rje d+r+wa ba'i 'od ces bya ba rdzogs so //
